translate English day7_hk_32f73919:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'd lost track of time as I stood beneath the shower spray, and I reach for the faucet to turn it off."


translate English day7_hk_447a3149:


    "As soon as the rumble of water pouring down on my head dies down, the room becomes deathly silent. {w}It's already night."


translate English day7_hk_d00d3732:


    et "I step out of the shower stall and take a deep breath of air, my cold lips trembling."


translate English day7_hk_6317dd21:



    nvl clear
    "\n The deserted temple is eerily quiet. {w}As I walk down the straight hallway, I absently glance out one of the windows and notice a white light."


translate English day7_hk_7af61df4:


    et "I find it uncomfortable on days when the sun doesn't set. {w}Because I feel like I have no place to hide. Which is why I continue on my way without faltering."


translate English day7_hk_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_hk_6bc08f8f:


    "\n I feel a breeze ruffle my still damp hair, making me realize I'm outside."


translate English day7_hk_25de875a:


    et "By abandoning one's body to the chill air, it tricks the mind into believing the body is cleaner than it really is."


translate English day7_hk_a5de1a68:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'm often accused of being way too sarcastic and unpleasant, but there are some things I enjoy. {w}Like nighttime, for example."


translate English day7_hk_6c7bde52:


    et "You don't have to work, you can relax and rest your tired body, and you can also take a shower. {w}Nighttime is when you can really take care of yourself."


translate English day7_hk_ea91f1c3:



    nvl clear
    "\n I also like the temple and my current job."


translate English day7_hk_1477f2d0:


    "By all rights, I should be living a cowardly and disgusting life out on the streets, feasting on the scraps from other people's discarded meals tossed in the trash."


translate English day7_hk_3ef51e67:


    "The temple gathers these lost children, fills their empty noggins with knowledge, puts tools in their wretched hands, and puts them to work for the sake of the nation."


translate English day7_hk_a69c2674:


    et "How wonderful!"


translate English day7_hk_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_hk_7c6cb1cf:


    et "\n Now then... {w}Where should I go?"


translate English day7_hkR_979c9754:


    nar "If you push past the overgrown weeds, you'll be able to catch that bitter, albeit faint, scent unique to tree nuts. You'll also see a building."


translate English day7_hkR_38bf72c8:


    nar "It's a solitary chapel tucked away within the forest, with no trace of any human footprints."


translate English day7_hkR_fa6a4373:


    nar "It exudes a reverential and somewhat forbidding air that preserves its former glory."


translate English day7_hkR_b3fa91e3:


    nar "You have to turn the old doorknob, which has seen better days, as hard as possible in order to get inside."


translate English day7_hkR_9362d8cb:


    nar "The unlocked door opens with a heavy and tired creak, and shortly after, wind begins to gradually fill the inside of the chapel."


translate English day7_hkR_183c5ac6:


    nar "She's standing there."


translate English day7_hkR_04a46ea7:


    nar "She has her hands clasped together before the blessing of the radiant sun that never sets, clearly praying for something."


translate English day7_hkR_b605fe99:


    nar "Each strand of her pure-white hair sparkles under the light, illuminated by it. Her hair follows the smooth line of her profile, from her well-slopped shoulders down her back."


translate English day7_hkR_9b806626:


    nar "Small dust motes float in the air, glistening within the sun's rays."


translate English day7_hkR_2921b8e5:


    nar "The door that has protected this sublime space for so long closes once more with a heavy thud. It's then she slowly turns to face me."


translate English day7_hkR_3dc945a6:


    nar "Her eyes, hidden beneath long eyelashes, glow golden in the light,"


translate English day7_hkR_7a4a4c0e:


    nar "though as soon as she steps within the shadow where I'm standing, they return to blue."


translate English day7_hkR_f6f12e6c:


    nar "I lower my face, not wanting to see my reflection in those eyes, and she immediately places the fingers of one hand under my chin."


translate English day7_hkR_cc553d1a:


    nar "Those big, blue eyes are almost dazzlingly cool."


translate English day7_hkR_4e3b66c4:


    hk_b "You look terrible."


translate English day7_hkR_449cad45:


    nar "I prefer the night. {w}I can close my eyes in peace, use the shower without worrying other people might be there, and walk through the quiet temple halls."


translate English day7_hkR_3162ae30:


    nar "Though I'm never actually alone."


translate English day7_hkR_92a8a02d:


    hk_b "Securett."


translate English day7_hkR_65d762bc:


    nar "I've been meeting Haku Eckaran in secret."


translate English day7_hkR_3f45f7b7:



    nvl clear
    "\n I grew up in a small village which housed the dregs who couldn't make it in the capital."


translate English day7_hkR_277f1dff:


    "My family was pretty average. {w}Compromised of a woman who gave birth at an early age and the man who loved her."


translate English day7_hkR_876857c1:


    et "I lived with the two of them like a freeloader for about eleven years."


translate English day7_hkR_e0261cd0:



    nvl clear
    "\n We were poor, and yet I was happy enough. Why? Because I loved my family."


translate English day7_hkR_3f4e465f:


    "Though now I realize that happiness I felt was nothing more than an illusion brought on by the innocence of youth. {w}Thankfully, I wasn't aware of my own mediocrity at the time."


translate English day7_hkR_c80c9e0e:


    "It was around the time I finally saw my mom for the pathetic person she was as our family disintegrated."


translate English day7_hkR_7778b056:


    "Her beloved brother cut ties with the rest of the family, which included me as well. {w}I was left with nothing but a piece of identification and a pitiful amount of money."


translate English day7_hkR_abd56276:


    "As a kid from the slums, my need for money directly translated to a desire to survive. I worked to live. {w}But my soul was already dead."


translate English day7_hkR_0b8a5e0c:



    nvl clear
    "\n That's what led to the birth of the priest known as Securett Rafe."


translate English day7_hkR_67125760:


    et "Instead of the yellow identification card, too mortifying to show in public, I began my new life brandishing a silver cross representing the glory of God."


translate English day7_hkR_78995362:


    hk_b "Hey, knock it off with the daydreaming. You'll catch a cold."


translate English day7_hkR_a0853415:


    sc "I was just thinking. {w}And if I catch a cold then that just means it's too cold in here..."


translate English day7_hkR_5ca18157:


    hk_b "The swelling on your face won't go down without the help of a cold breeze. {w}My word! A girl of your age shouldn't go around with a face that filthy."


translate English day7_hkR_18186917:


    hk_b "Are you trying to make our Holy Mother who art in Heaven sad?"


translate English day7_hkR_5dfa65ca:


    nar "Isn't it supposed to be our Father who art in Heaven?"


translate English day7_hkR_1653789c:


    sc "My face isn't always filthy, Haku. {w}You may be a bishop, but that doesn't excuse the bizarre things you always say to me."


translate English day7_hkR_89472f75:


    hk_b "I'm just trying to add a little pinch of joy to your otherwise humdrum temple life."


translate English day7_hkR_6651671e:


    hk_b "And yet your amusement seems to fade with each passing day."


translate English day7_hkR_4132de84:


    sc "Are you that bored?"


translate English day7_hkR_f8e1d308:


    hk_b "See? That's exactly what I'm talking about. Truly, the time spent outside of our joyless conversations..."


translate English day7_hkR_6e2b08a2:


    nar "Where are my manners. This lady before me is Haku Eckaran."


translate English day7_hkR_8f0e6b88:


    nar "Her daylight appearance, sparkling beneath the brilliantly shining light like gold, is nothing more than an illusion she created herself,"


translate English day7_hkR_1212f8b4:


    nar "with her true appearance hidden amongst the shadows, like so."


translate English day7_hkR_8d062d79:


    nar "Haku is a person of action, preferring that over thoughts and prayers. She strongly believes helping others with her own hands rather than relying on God."


translate English day7_hkR_d1778efe:


    nar "However, her almost stream-of-conscious-esque manner of speaking and bad habits left her seemingly unfit for a position as bishop,"


translate English day7_hkR_cae7b3c6:


    nar "which is why I've been charged with keeping an eye on her most of the time. {w}That is the secret we share."


translate English day7_hkR_97fb5aae:


    nar "The only time she can be her true self is during these secret meetings in the middle of the night--and I'm her chosen companion."


translate English day7_hkR_3a899a13:


    sc "I thought your hobby was pretending to be Pestis clad in a human disguise..."


translate English day7_hkR_766437c0:


    sc "while freaking the naive new recruits by babbling nonsense and speaking in tongues?"


translate English day7_hkR_ebbde255:


    hk_b "I have no idea what you're talking about. {w}Besides, I gave that up a while ago. There's never a good opportunity to do so, anyway."


translate English day7_hkR_8f528353:


    hk_b "I had a script all written out and everything."


translate English day7_hkR_a49754b8:


    sc "If only you showed as much enthusiasm for your actual work..."


translate English day7_hkR_cc1d8791:


    hk_b "I knew he'd find me one day."


translate English day7_hkR_42aed8d3:


    nar "The outdoor chapel that we meet in every night has always been off-limits to the temple priests, though occasionally, a brave soul will wander in."


translate English day7_hkR_50e33b7c:


    nar "I personally don't find those occurrences all that gratifying."


translate English day7_hkR_c04b83f7:


    sc "Oh, right. You're talking about [na2], hrm? You've taken an unexpected liking to him."


translate English day7_hkR_79f70112:


    hk_b "I would say it's less about any kind of interest and more how simply striking he is as a person."


translate English day7_hkR_56c844ac:


    hk_b "Just like you."


translate English day7_hkR_8ada0508:


    sc "Was he here again?"


translate English day7_hkR_efb10f63:


    hk_b "No, so don't scowl at me like that. {w}You're only making your filthy face look even worse."


translate English day7_hkR_8aed9559:


    sc "I don't want other people intruding on our space..."


translate English day7_hkR_ff4877cf:


    sc "I know you're bored, but you really need to exercise more caution than you do already."


translate English day7_hkR_5e12f69b:


    sc "For being off-limits, this place is surprisingly easy to get into."


translate English day7_hkR_3b2e0f1e:


    sc "Placing something off-limits only makes people more intrigued anyways--especially naive new recruits who don't know any better."


translate English day7_hkR_a9a557dd:


    hk_b "That's enough. A secret can make one feel safe by its mere existence alone."


translate English day7_hkR_613b0bdd:


    sc "And since that alone isn't enough to assuage anxiety, they end up buried under a mount of secrets."


translate English day7_hkR_dc4ebffa:


    hk_b "From the sound of it, you seem to like this place a lot."


translate English day7_hkR_a86b7bc8:


    sc "I've just grown used to it... This place is decidedly off-limits. There's no way I could ever like it."


translate English day7_hkR_88973d68:


    hk_b "You're far too sentimental. I know you could never hate it either."


translate English day7_hkR_873dee0f:


    sc "Which is exactly why I'm saying we need to be more careful."


translate English day7_hkR_8cadc849:


    sc "If someone happened to find us here, you have no idea how they might read the situation."


translate English day7_hkR_1d86162d:


    hk_b "It's not exactly what it looks like?"


translate English day7_hkR_3fd04b54:


    sc "And what exactly *does* it look like?"


translate English day7_hkR_5fda5145:


    hk_b "An untrustworthy person who was hired under false pretenses and the dimwitted bishop who enjoys their company."


translate English day7_hkR_e91c95cf:


    hk_b "That's what you're trying to say, right?"


translate English day7_hkR_1036756a:


    sc "Something like that..."


translate English day7_hkR_f968a9b9:


    nar "I met Haku about nine months ago under circumstances so coincidental that you couldn't make it up."


translate English day7_hkR_3a1db230:


    nar "For a woman as unsuited to living the life of a hermit as she is, even the stupidest new recruits grew suspicious."


translate English day7_hkR_1e6d5112:


    nar "When she first invited me to meet her in this outdoor chapel, I was fairly nonplussed by the location."


translate English day7_hkR_5de4949a:


    nar "I found myself horrified at the putrid garbage left abandoned next to the open pit where corpses had been left to rot."


translate English day7_hkR_e6b9c3a0:


    nar "But it quickly became a daily routine of ours, to the point where I often come here by myself due to its familiarity."


translate English day7_hkR_cb777e0f:


    hk_b "You don't have to worry. There's no danger of anyone coming here for the time being. I plan on lighting a fire in that hole there in a moment."


translate English day7_hkR_cc0eaa56:


    sc "That hole? I hadn't realized there was that much trash built up... {w}I've heard of people doing so, but have never seen it happen personally."


translate English day7_hkR_51b80d4e:


    hk_b "Yep. We're usually not here when it does. {w}It's cold... Let's head inside?"


translate English day7_hkR_e38220b5:


    nar "The door is the same as always, and yet when I enter the chapel with Haku, it also seems so much lighter. We always chat in here."


translate English day7_hkR_d60c2771:


    nar "Despite how bright it still is outside, she always seems bathed in shadows, as if the sun itself is avoiding shining on her."


translate English day7_hkR_f3d7bda7:


    nar "Her eyes sink into blue within the darkness. I feel like I'm finally where I belong, and my emotions settle down along with her eye color."


translate English day7_hkR_95dff5e0:


    hk_b "So, how'd it go today? Did you have a fight with your friend? {w}Hm?"


translate English day7_hkR_2b4ab9b1:


    sc "Let go of me..."


translate English day7_hkR_56af557b:


    nar "I feel her hand on my back, pushing me forward lightly. At its urging, I sit down in the coldness."


translate English day7_hkR_bc42a928:


    nar "I'm not good at so-called \"gossip,\" yet in direct contrast, Haku genuinely enjoys talking about other people."


translate English day7_hkR_b2657919:


    nar "She always has something to say, which is why I spend most of the time listening to her..."


translate English day7_hkR_25e9d5c9:


    nar "Though lately it seems she's constantly trying to get me to talk, perhaps bored of always being the one to talk."


translate English day7_hkR_a2b93f8e:


    hk_b "From the looks of it, I think I hit the nail on the head. I'm not sure what to say other than congrats."


translate English day7_hkR_f76b4bd3:


    hk_b "I didn't really want you to get too friendly with those two."


translate English day7_hkR_ffd9e544:


    nar "If only those words held a hint of something like jealousy or envy."


translate English day7_hkR_a21d5be6:


    nar "But I know what she really means is more akin to the company you keep reflects back on you, and in this case, having unreliable friends in the Disposal Squad makes you an idiot."


translate English day7_hkR_d6a53541:


    nar "Much to my chagrin, I agree with her."


translate English day7_hkR_d9d10631:


    sc "By \"those two,\" I'm assuming you mean the new recruits who just started?"


translate English day7_hkR_b9e120db:


    hk_b "Who else? {w}Even you're aware of how much you stand out, I'm sure. Those two latched onto you as soon as they arrived."


translate English day7_hkR_606d5489:


    hk_b "You were angry for the first few days, but also strangely happy. You seemed distracted whenever we talked,"


translate English day7_hkR_0dd25855:


    hk_b "and you were late getting here from cleaning up after their mistakes. To make matters worse, you show up today looking like *that*..."


translate English day7_hkR_77791284:


    sc "..."


translate English day7_hkR_c51c86eb:


    hk_b "You're avoiding me... Now, is that how you treat your companions?"


translate English day7_hkR_9bf7a268:


    sc "Why do I get the feeling you're enjoying this, Haku?"


translate English day7_hkR_d77c2083:


    hk_b "Like I said earlier, I just wanted to congratulate you."


translate English day7_hkR_5f8176d8:


    hk_b "But if you're feeling sad and just want to be here, then I'll do what I can to comfort you."


translate English day7_hkR_44f30f64:


    sc "Sad? {w}I'm... {w}not that sad, actually."


translate English day7_hkR_800ae7bf:


    sc "I feel like there's been some kind of misunderstanding... {w}I was never all that close to those two."


translate English day7_hkR_7151fb49:


    sc "The frequency of our conversations simply reached the point where I knew I couldn't fool them any longer. They were going to find out the truth sooner or later..."


translate English day7_hkR_a3fe8e6f:


    sc "Honestly, I was kind of relieved..."


translate English day7_hkR_91698b60:


    nar "I'm speaking calmly, and yet for some reason, my heart's pounding in my ears. I let out a deep sigh, hoping it'll hurry up and quiet down."


translate English day7_hkR_9ad276a0:


    hk_b "Yeah? {w}Well, to be fair, you're a pretty bad liar."


translate English day7_hkR_ff93a350:


    sc "It's a little too late for that, don't you think?"


translate English day7_hkR_b7d225a2:


    sc "The only thing that matters is he'll be with us in the Cleanup Department for another month."


translate English day7_hkR_032586ed:


    sc "During which time the Magic Department won't see any new recruits, though."


translate English day7_hkR_0aacde4b:


    sc "we'll be able to observe the changes in his stigmata from a slightly closer vantage point."


translate English day7_hkR_68cf1d6a:


    hk_b "That seems fairly heavy-handed. Did you do this on purpose?"


translate English day7_hkR_d080bff1:


    sc "I swear... What happened was nothing more than an honest mistake..."


translate English day7_hkR_e9bb338a:


    sc "But as long as this is how I truly feel, then I can't be friends with him."


translate English day7_hkR_8dfa6dd8:


    hk_b "You pulled a pretty boneheaded move to get him to stay."


translate English day7_hkR_cb1d7d16:


    sc "Because you swore he had to go."


translate English day7_hkR_8d6673e0:


    hk_b "Ha. Ha. Ha. {w}I'm only a bishop because I was forced into this position. Don't confuse me for a pseudo-prophet."


translate English day7_hkR_7ee83109:


    hk_b "But, well... It's easy enough to fool someone as young as him, and I figured he'd get so caught up in playing pretend that he wouldn't notice..."


translate English day7_hkR_bfa59976:


    hk_b "But I get the feeling he knows more than he lets on."


translate English day7_hkR_398e0b20:


    nar "The Cleanup Department is a tough place, and it's impossible to make it out with one's juvenile mentality intact. {w}Which is why it holds a somewhat odd aura."


translate English day7_hkR_bc1dae9e:


    nar "It's too painful at times, enough so that when I find even the slightest connection to someone, it's all too easy to mistake it for love."


translate English day7_hkR_8dd8b2ad:


    nar "That she truly thought he could leave the department without any sort of unresolved emotions... {w}it's downright idiotic."


translate English day7_hkR_73fca123:


    hk_b "Either way... you must be relieved. {w}A critical time period is coming up. You need to focus on that."


translate English day7_hkR_8ac46ecf:


    nar "Haku's voice softens, as if noticing the way my mouth is screwed shut."


translate English day7_hkR_ca2ffe81:


    nar "Instead of celebrating what she had been doing, she switches to comfort. My pounding heartbeat regains its former serene state of being."


translate English day7_hkR_90030f9c:


    nar "Whenever she tells me a hard truth, she always makes sure to follow it up with words I actually want to hear."


translate English day7_hkR_f961b7a0:


    nar "...Though a part of me hates myself for reacting exactly the way she wants me to."


translate English day7_hkR_1a204b67:


    sc "I know full well without you telling me. {w}I'm planning on refocusing on my work starting tomorrow."


translate English day7_hkR_f348f577:


    sc "Dealing with everything today took up most of my time. I have to make sure that doesn't happen again."


translate English day7_hkR_eec0b434:


    nar "I'm turning over a new leaf, so to speak."


translate English day7_hkR_e509c83c:


    nar "As stated earlier, we need him to stay here for the time being so as not to give the Magic Department an advantage they could use against the Cleanup Department."


translate English day7_hkR_634e11bc:


    nar "Then there's the matter of wanting to meddle in Erzsebet's plans, and give us more time to observe his stigmata."


translate English day7_hkR_5589df8f:


    nar "I'm also planning on becoming an official priest and the auxiliary bishop of the Cleanup Department this year on Christmas Eve."


translate English day7_hkR_f8708176:


    sc "I'm pretty busy. But I'm only going to get even busier moving forward."


translate English day7_hkR_02b89484:


    sc "I guess I got distracted since up until now, I've always had at least a little leeway."


translate English day7_hkR_51db5942:


    hk_b "You're an oddball for sure. Most people don't hope for more work. {w}They ask for more time off."


translate English day7_hkR_85ab0e1f:


    sc "I don't really care if I'm normal or not, Haku."


translate English day7_hkR_c16d97c4:


    sc "If you look at it with your best interests in mind, then doesn't my working more hours make your life more convenient?"


translate English day7_hkR_2377cc2d:


    hk_b "Perhaps. Though that individualistic thinking will someday lead to the birth of an organization."


translate English day7_hkR_77791284_1:


    sc "..."


translate English day7_hkR_0bde17c8:


    hk_b "There's one thing I must ask, though... About the new recruit. What is it about the situation that drives you to work as hard as you do?"


translate English day7_hkR_941ae358:


    nar "Me? {w}The reason why I work so hard is that..."


translate English day7_hkR_67f766ef:


    sc "I'm doing it for you, of course. It's why I do anything for the department and why I kept him here... {w}Seems a little late to ask."


translate English day7_hkR_e0dc5ad9:


    nar "After hearing my answer, Haku remains silent for a moment."


translate English day7_hkR_d6f22417:


    nar "She has a habit of suddenly falling silent before simply smiling at me."


translate English day7_hkR_91ad7a06:


    nar "It's not the same smile she wears when amused, and I find myself falling silent alongside her."


translate English day7_hkR_cc1c9414:


    hk_b "Do you know why you've spent so much time with me until now?"


translate English day7_hkR_9bb59e8b:


    sc "Well... Because you're my boss?"


translate English day7_hkR_0c28e1b8:


    hk_b "That's more or less correct."


translate English day7_hkR_a91e573b:


    nar "Am I wrong? Haku is pretty easy to understand most of the time, but I feel like I'm missing something."


translate English day7_hkR_11deab03:


    sc "It should be obvious I'm doing it for the money."


translate English day7_hkR_e2bbda17:


    hk_b "Yeah? Even though becoming an auxiliary bishop won't net you much of a pay raise?"


translate English day7_hkR_8c649775:


    sc "Why ask for an answer if you're just going to argue with me? {w}You know my workaholic personality is all about making as much money as possible, even now..."


translate English day7_hkR_8bce1400:


    sc "Is that the only reason for your auxiliary aspirations?"


translate English day7_hkR_2f327f56:


    hk_b "I have a feeling even you're aware how ridiculous that excuse sounds, right?"


