    hk_b "Isn't that sad? {w}Every one of us is supposed to be the main character in the story of their own life,"


translate English day7_hkR_8d4b2915:


    hk_b "and yet the world remains unchanged and foul. Someone has to take care of the mess that other people leave behind, right?"


translate English day7_hkR_a3c6ac11:


    hk_b "With that said, I don't think anyone dreams of doing this for the rest of their lives."


translate English day7_hkR_dbd8c35c:


    sc "You're right... It's a job no one wants."


