    sc "And yet this is what I want to do. The Cleanup Department's purpose is about helping people, saving them."


translate English day7_hkR_dfe03e20:


    sc "If there's even a glimmer of value in what I do, then it's all worth it."


translate English day7_hkR_0dacf1d1:


    hk_b "Well said. That's why I like you so much."


translate English day7_hkR_652265e3:


    hk_b "When you say \"it's a tough job, but someone's gotta do it,\" it's less about hating the work you do and more about how much you want to get it done."


translate English day7_hkR_a4480132:


    sc "You speak as if it's someone else's problem. You're the one who taught me that view point."


translate English day7_hkR_32033a6a:


    hk_b "Yeah? I guess I did."


translate English day7_hkR_b1f72169:


    nar "Haku has, in fact, taught me a great deal."


