    sc "Is there anything that's changed since then, other than my hair?"


translate English day7_hkR_1a262a1a:


    hk_b "Hmm."


translate English day7_hkR_0d779d36:


    nar "She says while averting her gaze. She tends to do that whenever she's trying to recall the past."


translate English day7_hkR_247d2723:


    hk_b "You're calmer now, and much more composed."


translate English day7_hkR_932c9594:


    sc "You're far more efficient as well."


translate English day7_hkR_c8a1366e:


    hk_b "Would it be a compliment if I said you no longer seem affected by death and the insignificant sorrow that accompanies it? {w}You don't seem to cry, no matter the situation."


translate English day7_hkR_72d94a50:


    hk_b "Do you remember the day of your first surgical procedure? {w}You cut your hair and got brand new clothes."


translate English day7_hkR_63924636:


    hk_b "You were harassed at the funeral since everyone but you had died."


translate English day7_hkR_55da08e4:


    nar "Every time Haku recounts a moment from the past, she acts like a doctor treating a patient with amnesia."


translate English day7_hkR_7a508db1:


    nar "Of course, my memories are still very much intact--which is why I never know how to respond to her when she treats me this way."


translate English day7_hkR_13db4196:


    hk_b "I honestly expected you to scream or cry at any moment. Like any normal child would given the circumstances."


translate English day7_hkR_86169aa9:


    hk_b "But you didn't shed even one tear. It was a complete shift from the way you would have reacted up until that day."


translate English day7_hkR_2db360a3:


    sc "Is that bad?"


translate English day7_hkR_6a5d73e2:


    hk_b "I'm sorry you feel that way. {w}But it's actually the opposite."


translate English day7_hkR_180fb453:


    hk_b "When I saw you like that, I felt you'd grown stronger. And I was proud of your growth."


translate English day7_hkR_c11c5054:


    sc "Ahem..."


translate English day7_hkR_80653a2b:


    hk_b "You weren't expecting me to pay you a compliment, were you?"


translate English day7_hkR_7ee850b1:


    nar "I thought I knew everything there was to know about her, but I guess there are still facets of her personality that are a mystery to me."


translate English day7_hkR_da5d8b4c:


    nar "And vice versa. She acts as if she knows me like the back of her hand, and yet I still have the ability to surprise her on occasion."


translate English day7_hkR_4d9efde4:


    hk_b "What do you plan on doing moving forward?"


translate English day7_hkR_b15c463b:


    sc "The same as usual. I'm not sure what you were hoping for, but if it's amusement, you'll have to look elsewhere. {w}What do you want to do for dinner?"


translate English day7_hkR_7ca22ecd:


    hk_b "Let's go out. {w}I want alcohol! And meat! Definitely meat!"


translate English day7_hkR_348ec109:


    hk_b "...Which is what I'd like to say, but we should probably keep things low-key. I still have work to do."


translate English day7_hkR_88639f28:


    sc "You still haven't finished for the day? {w}I had... no idea, honestly."


translate English day7_hkR_79ad43ab:


    hk_b "Is that so?"


translate English day7_hkR_5265ded0:


    nar "Haku is a chatterbox, but she never says the stuff I really want to hear."


translate English day7_hkR_d92da102:


    nar "I will most likely never find out if the words kept locked within her tight-lipped mouth are things better left unsaid,"


translate English day7_hkR_74463198:


    nar "or things I shouldn't know about at all."


