    sc "Will you be here tomorrow as well, Haku?"


translate English day7_hkR_0b9b26b4:


    nar "I decide to change the topic with a question. {w}It's the same question I ask right before it's time for us to part ways."


translate English day7_hkR_4f1b6be2:


    nar "The question itself should feel natural enough after all this time, so why is my hand shaking? I'm sure it has everything to do with her current demeanor."


