    hk_b "Of course. I'm the one who always asks you to meet me, right? {w}So please come here tomorrow. We can have another nice chat."


translate English day7_hkR_1c607162:


    nar "Haku always responds as if hearing that question for the first time, and always with the same words. Perhaps in hopes of training me."


