translate English day8_hk_8787a273:


    hk_b "I find there is nothing more interesting in the world than re-reading prose one has written while in a comatose state."


translate English day8_hk_60c21c9b:


    hk_b "It's like a badly written bible or a love letter."


translate English day8_hk_fd7f41ff:


    sc "Did you bring it here for me to see it?"


