    sc "That she was worried about you... {w}That's all."


translate English day8_hk_f107c74e:


    nar "She seems pleased, even though that's all we discussed."


translate English day8_hk_5ca9eece:


    nar "She's lived longer than I have, and I will never have a part in anything that happened before I entered her life,"


translate English day8_hk_c92d815e:


    nar "but regardless, she seems to enjoy knowing there are people around her who worry about her."


translate English day8_hk_31f2eb4e:


    sc "The bishop of the Health Department shared the same sentiment."


translate English day8_hk_01f25ca4:


    hk_b "Don't drag down a nice story concerning a fair maiden by mentioning a cranky old coot."


translate English day8_hk_96612f06:


    nar "If that's her attitude towards him, Bishop Gregor must have it pretty rough..."


translate English day8_hk_f13170f3:


    hk_b "I don't care about that old fart. The doctor was worried about me, huh?"


translate English day8_hk_690fc6c7:


    extend " Hs! She really said that? Hee hee hee!"


