    sc "By the way, as of late, it's been happening in the afternoon as well."


translate English day8_hk_88473625:


    hk_b "I know all too well. Not like it matters, since it's just as bright in the afternoon as the night."


translate English day8_hk_41a39836:


    hk_b "I hate having to quietly listen while that old geezer in the Magic Department prattles on with his inane lectures. {w}With the way I'm feeling lately, I can't deal with it as well as I usually do."


translate English day8_hk_fb030c3a:


    sc "Did your new girlfriend dump you or something?"


