    hk_b "Tsk! What are you talking about? {w}I thought you moved beyond such remarks when you graduated from school?"


translate English day8_hk_e613d7f3:


    hk_b "Like I've told you before... You're all I have, Securett."


translate English day8_hk_8ff3ed93:


    nar "She manages to close one eye with some difficulty before blowing me a loud kiss."


translate English day8_hk_fef76d2e:


    nar "She always does this, despite being unable to wink properly."


translate English day8_hk_f9bd2221:


    hk_b "Your seemingly cold and disinterested reaction never fails to turn me on..."


translate English day8_hk_478aa8f9:


    sc "And your terrible jokes never fail to make me cringe."


translate English day8_hk_4f81a644:


    hk_b "Here we go again. You really do make me happy, you know."


translate English day8_hk_f0eea374:


    sc "Knock it off already... {w}Are you still having problems with the bishop of the Magic Department?"


