    hk_b "It originally belonged to Bishop Eri, and he often held tea parties there for the three of us."


translate English day8_hk_cec7ff31:


    hk_b "He was a kind man, even to a stubborn jerk like my younger self. {w}But thinking back... I have no idea why Eri even bothered to come."


translate English day8_hk_b89d2c1d:


    hk_b "He'd just sit there, silently sipping tea."


translate English day8_hk_f70f11ab:


    hk_b "Though occasionally he'd place a gift or a snack in his younger brother's hand."


translate English day8_hk_a189980c:


    hk_b "Even when we made eye contact, he wouldn't say a word..."


translate English day8_hk_4ca5124b:


    hk_b "Perhaps that was his way of showing affection."


translate English day8_hk_a73ca5f3:


    sc "Yeah?"


translate English day8_hk_2dd76bcf:


    hk_b "Well, it didn't last very long. {w}Father wasn't a huge fan."


translate English day8_hk_c953a541:


    hk_b "What with the whole frolicking in gardens and munching on sweets, you know."


translate English day8_hk_7b0969d5:


    hk_b "At any rate, I liked Eri a lot better back then. He's become a bit of a glib know-it-all in his old age."


translate English day8_hk_879c9f19:


    sc "Speaking of which, I heard he paid a visit to the office recently."


translate English day8_hk_cc3adbe0:


    hk_b "Oh, you can be sure I didn't hold back!"


translate English day8_hk_442d03ad:


    hk_b "It was somewhat inevitable, though I feel he's become excessively intrusive ever since our department has fallen under their jurisdiction."


translate English day8_hk_27510e95:


    hk_b "I appreciate the unwelcome favor I never asked for, you old codger."


translate English day8_hk_fd89d9ca:


    hk_b "I've long since grown past the age where a simple gift is enough to cheer me up."


translate English day8_hk_76b80daf:


    nar "Despite her words, Haku seems to enjoy reminiscing about their shared past."


translate English day8_hk_941dc399:


    nar "Though hearing her talk like this makes me feel as if I'm learning more than I really need to know."


translate English day8_hk_511f75cc:


    hk_b "With that said... I'd be lying if I said I didn't respect him at all. {w}He has this way of setting the perfect mood through the way he wields words alone."


translate English day8_hk_eac0ac9b:


    sc "You don't hear people talk like that now a days. {w}That sort of... cumbersome and antiquated method of speech."


translate English day8_hk_b1706567:


    hk_b "It's honestly kind of like a game to him..."


translate English day8_hk_964f8d4c:


    hk_b "As long as the other person can't figure out what you're trying to say, then you don't have to work out a script."


translate English day8_hk_6ee3e99d:


    sc "Right. I'm sorry..."


translate English day8_hk_42c938ee:


    hk_b "But also... He was marvelous at teaching children."


translate English day8_hk_4a1573c4:


    hk_b "Especially the eldest daughter, who you knew had the gift of magic just by looking at her."


translate English day8_hk_237e54ea:


    hk_b "The last time I saw her was during the funeral for that one child's father. Ah, she has certainly turned into a fine young lady..."


translate English day8_hk_f974b699:


    hk_b "Though she was a real crybaby growing up, I assure."


translate English day8_hk_91ecce76:


    hk_b "So few people are aware of that fact. It's one I feel honored to know, heh heh."


translate English day8_hk_ae19b8c2:


    sc "Have you ever tried talking to her directly?"


translate English day8_hk_63549079:


    hk_b "Mm, no... Not... directly... {w}But when you watch them for long enough, you grow a certain fondness for them."


translate English day8_hk_c243764e:


    hk_b "Even if the emotions felt are one-sided at best... {w}She does seem like she'd be quite understanding and a great conversation partner."


translate English day8_hk_9b89201d:


    hk_b "I look forward to the day when we can finally meet, face-to-face. {w}If such a day ever comes."


translate English day8_hk_9728cbcf:


    sc "You speak as if that might never happen."


translate English day8_hk_89750acf:


    hk_b "You never know..."


