translate English day8_hk_2321848f:


    nar "The only reason we talk to each other is because we have no one else."


translate English day8_hk_9c970ed6:


    nar "Which is why questions such as \"why exactly are you telling me this?\""


translate English day8_hk_84a31a70:


    nar "or deliberate misunderstandings are taboo. {w}Why try to seek logic in illogical actions?"


