    sc "Isn't it a bit early to be thinking about next year? {w}It's still summer."


translate English day8_hk_0cdc444e:


    hk_b "Says the person who began looking forward to Christmas Eve in spring."


translate English day8_hk_155dc29e:


    sc "That's simply because Christmas Eve is when I'll finally officially become an auxiliary bishop."


translate English day8_hk_773dcc70:


    hk_b "As a sinner, you must pay penance accordingly, though you'll be free once that's done."


translate English day8_hk_45d2107a:


    hk_b "You'll have a marvelous coming of age ceremony."


