    sc "What about the guy known as Securett who already had his coming of age ceremony?"


translate English day8_hk_01a6cf08:


    hk_b "That man is not you. {w}You'll receive new clothes and be able to live life as a brand new woman."


translate English day8_hk_cf34f3c9:


    sc "Uh... Wow." with sshake


translate English day8_hk_3065a6d1:


    hk_b "I figured you'd give me a reaction far from anything I could have imagined."


translate English day8_hk_31196746:


    sc "Whatever role you give me, I'll do what I can as your subordinate to meet your expectations..."


translate English day8_hk_2c57cd4e:


    sc "But I still don't know about any of that. We've been fooling everyone around us for far too long."


translate English day8_hk_f5d4ac6a:


    hk_b "We have no other choice but to keep our secrets, though that doesn't equate to sinning in the process."


translate English day8_hk_f440bf5b:


    hk_b "There's something in your features that's changed since we first met... {w}You don't want to actually spend the rest of your life as a man, right?"


translate English day8_hk_c9e2acb5:


    sc "I know that... But I feel like it's too late. {w}The problem is I've lied to everyone who ever trusted me."


translate English day8_hk_3c5bc218:


    hk_b "Something did happen, didn't it?"


translate English day8_hk_1eab1f97:


    nar "I thought she was acting weird earlier. Was she, in fact, was probing me for information?"


translate English day8_hk_8785452e:


    nar "The incident in question has long since passed, and I honestly don't really want to talk about it..."


translate English day8_hk_8b73698a:


    sc "It concerns [na]. Though I'm sure you're already aware..."


translate English day8_hk_3452cf9f:


    sc "I thought I had him fooled, but I was wrong."


translate English day8_hk_105b6f8b:


    sc "He'd been waiting all this time for me to come clean with him, believing I would,"


translate English day8_hk_1f99d96a:


    sc "and when I didn't, he saw me as a traitor."


translate English day8_hk_c10ca7ed:


    sc "Especially after he confided in me..."


translate English day8_hk_3c1ffc0a:


    hk_b "Your bad habit is acting as if nothing you do can ever be forgiven. {w}That's how you ended up with the messed-up face yesterday?"


translate English day8_hk_25465804:


    sc "Yes. That was the penance he felt I had to pay for the crime of stabbing him in the back."


translate English day8_hk_365e1e32:


    sc "And yet, even after that, he's still angry..."


translate English day8_hk_054c9065:


    nar "Despite having enough of a headache over you already..."


translate English day8_hk_89eac9f5:


    sc "Meaning that even though I paid penance for the sin he says I've committed, I've still not gained my freedom... to use your choice of words."


translate English day8_hk_96a10819:


    hk_b "Are you sure that's not simply the weight of your guilt speaking?"


translate English day8_hk_35fac087:


    hk_b "No, that's not it. {w}Why do you tend to assume everything is your fault?"


translate English day8_hk_b1edadd5:


    hk_b "There's no question that you lied to him and thus betrayed his trust. You absolutely sinned in that regard."


translate English day8_hk_32469f8b:


    hk_b "But if there's a rational reason behind your actions, then you didn't do a bad thing at all. You, in fact, made the right decision."


translate English day8_hk_92eeb18e:


    sc "A part of me wonders if I should have just trusted him, like he trusted me."


translate English day8_hk_bd4fba19:


    hk_b "Even if you had, what are you going to do about it now?"


translate English day8_hk_7227566a:


    hk_b "If I'm not mistaken, you're the one who pontificated on the worth of your own will. {w}Don't doubt the decision you made."


translate English day8_hk_b8cf2467:


    sc "I dunno... I probably should have talked to you about it yesterday..."


translate English day8_hk_120db359:


    hk_b "Regardless, I knew you'd cough it up eventually."


translate English day8_hk_c78ed3fa:


    hk_b "He's not the only who's been patiently waiting for you to open that mouth of yours. {w}Bare your soul to me, sinner."


translate English day8_hk_c9135b26:


    sc "Ugh. Knock it off..."


translate English day8_hk_88d37cc0:


    sc "All those brothers and sisters in the Magic Department that you mentioned earlier, and Lavi..."


translate English day8_hk_69bee3bd:


    sc "They're all so kind to me, and I know that kindness would turn to hatred the instant they learned the truth."


translate English day8_hk_4b50916d:


    hk_b "Within your small circle of friends, you seem to be doing just fine."


translate English day8_hk_7cb90a53:


    sc "Then there's the matter of the priests in the Disposal Squad."


translate English day8_hk_83b3ed0d:


    hk_b "Since when did you start caring about something that unimportant?"


translate English day8_hk_d9bf22a1:


    sc "Look, all I'm saying is I have no idea how any of them will take it..."


translate English day8_hk_491db365:


    sc "You're saying you've never thought about it even once?"


translate English day8_hk_51539e1f:


    hk_b "Hmm... No, I have. {w}I mean, we all have our own secrets..."


translate English day8_hk_9f543f9b:


    hk_b "But, Securett..."


translate English day8_hk_08540b16:


    hk_b "Lying to people may be a sin, but you have a good reason for doing so, and a cast-iron goal."


translate English day8_hk_77e9b864:


    hk_b "I think it's far more rude to start doubting the decision you made out of guilt."


translate English day8_hk_4742f6a6:


    hk_b "Stand by your choices and be confident. {w}Why can't you do that?"


translate English day8_hk_70acd91c:


    sc "Who knows... Probably because I'm not strong like you."


translate English day8_hk_6111741f:


    sc "Of course I want to achieve the goals I've set for myself, and I don't think I've made the wrong choice in doing so..."


translate English day8_hk_92c51f06:


    sc "But..."


translate English day8_hk_18df9ebd:


    hk_b "You lack faith. {w}Fine... In that case, let me tell you something."


translate English day8_hk_6af83176:


    hk_b "You're doing the right thing. So just make sure you do what needs to be done."


translate English day8_hk_d2dfeab8:


    hk_b "I believe you can do it."


translate English day8_hk_caf3003c:


    sc "...Thanks."


translate English day8_hk_75d80aa4:


    nar "As we talk, the awkwardness from earlier disappears."


translate English day8_hk_d646309e:


    nar "There's no hint of hyperbole in her words. I know she's telling the truth."


translate English day8_hk_4e522f0a:


    nar "My dark desires and misfortune are trivial in light of this stroke of luck."


translate English day8_hk_6838382d:


    nar "And the pain born from everything that's happened thus far can be quickly soothed by sleep, food, and some nice conversation. But I have to over complicate everything."


translate English day8_hk_53461aa2:


    sc "Haku... Thank you."


translate English day8_hk_332a24e0:


    nar "I suddenly realize I haven't been communicating my feelings of gratitude that well lately, so I speak those words out loud."


translate English day8_hk_f4fe4485:


    nar "I can see Haku looking at me out of the corner of my eye with a puzzled expression on her face. I look away as well."


translate English day8_hk_36ef643b:


    sc "I-If you didn't hear me, then it doesn't matter!" with sshake


translate English day8_hk_88214c0d:


    hk_b "Ha ha ha! You're really funny. {w}I heard you, loud and clear. Thank you, too."


translate English day8_hk_a83d5b74:


    nar "She says while smiling, though I don't understand what she means by it."


translate English day8_hk_baf5d43d:


    nar "She's the one who helped me out, so why is she thanking me?"


translate English day8_hk_73823389:


    nar "The only thing I know for sure is that she seems to be in a better mood than before."


translate English day8_hk_d714d6ab:


    nar "Though I get the feeling she confided in me about something weighing on her mind just like I did to her."


translate English day8_hk_f6c779f2:


    sc "I guess I'll see you here tomorrow?"


translate English day8_hk_783e14c3:


    hk_b "Of course! I'm looking forward to talking with you."


translate English day8_hk_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_hk_3a1157b7:


    nar "I can't sleep at all..."


translate English day9_hk_d36e9a63:


    nar "I should apologize to Arnie the next chance I get. Good idea."


translate English day9_hk_3794ea57:


    nar "I don't see the violence wielded by my own hands as a sin. What the devil wants is for you to drown in your own tumultuous sea of emotions."


translate English day9_hk_a03c3c4a:


    nar "Is it really a sin to punish the devil himself? It seems obvious that a believer of God would strive to do so."


translate English day9_hk_0c6e7b4b:


    nar "The devil constantly tries to drag me down with all sorts of temptations, but I must remain in the present. I'm doing the best I can do."


translate English day9_hk_790a5af6:


    nar "I feel terrible. I haven't seen any sight of him today."


translate English day9_hk_7f590386:


    nar "And yet my own painful anxiety has been eating at me all day. Where the hell did I go wrong?"


translate English day9_hk_a083de89:


    nar "What if Haku doesn't come to the chapel today? {w}The thought suddenly crosses my mind."


translate English day9_hk_06b6ac5c:


    nar "I know that won't happen, but the thought alone makes me anxious."


translate English day9_hk_20249d51:


    nar "No matter how many secrets we share, she's someone that I'll never be able to get close to."


translate English day9_hk_0572596d:


    nar "The only time we can engage in childish conversations is at night, while during the day we work in silence together as a bishop and her subordinate."


translate English day9_hk_e0f4c319:


    nar "When I arrive, I don't find Haku in her usual spot, which only adds to my fear."


translate English day9_hk_8d9701e6:


    nar "I search the darkened forest paths and the shadows between the trees. She deliberately avoids the light, always seeking out the gloom."


translate English day9_hk_75f6f43d:


    nar "I personally don't think the darkness suits her, but she thinks otherwise."


translate English day9_hk_e2627cb4:


    nar "No matter where she is, it's almost like she isn't there at all."


translate English day9_hk_12e46fd8:


    hk_b "Bah!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_b06cacb5:


    sc "Whoa?!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_3ad5e371:


    hk_b "Hee hee hee... I took your advice and chose a different hiding spot today."


translate English day9_hk_78cf6cb5:


    hk_b "Despite acting like you know everything, you didn't see me at all."


translate English day9_hk_3475eb7e:


    hk_b "At any rate, what took you so long? {w}I thought I was going to die from boredom!"


translate English day9_hk_2fbd549a:


    sc "Uh... {w}Are you sure you're still alive? You kind of look otherwise... ha ha..."


translate English day9_hk_1a24492d:


    nar "Haku, who suddenly appeared in front of me, is bleeding. {w}There's fresh blood pouring down her stomach--or more accurately, from the side of her stomach."


translate English day9_hk_fcd1cd22:


    nar "That she popped up seemingly out of nowhere was surprising enough, but to have her jump out at me in the state she's in is even more so."


translate English day9_hk_75df3803:


    hk_b "Hee hee... All kinds of things happen when you're a bishop."


translate English day9_hk_eb1bfb8b:


    hk_b "This is far from enough to kill me, so no need to fret! Ha! Ha! Ha!"


translate English day9_hk_02e2235f:


    nar "The white clothes she'd just washed yesterday are stained bright red, and her black coat is covered in mud."


translate English day9_hk_b1202e99:


    nar "I felt anxious about the blood at first, but seeing her cracking jokes..."


translate English day9_hk_a5991e37:


    nar "...while blood poured down her side put me at ease, and I gradually begin calm down."


translate English day9_hk_efaf751f:


    nar "I immediately open the door to the chapel." with sshake


translate English day9_hk_24dbf9dc:


    nar "The sound of the heavy door swinging open echoes loudly, the wind that bursts forth fluttering Haku's long hair."


translate English day9_hk_7c0ec639:


    nar "Her laughter suddenly stops."


translate English day9_hk_16dd74eb:


    nar "Her look of surprise gradually changes to one of discontent, and she obediently follows me inside."


translate English day9_hk_35c8a6d8:


    hk_b "You're not a kitten wagging its tail, so don't hiss at me when you're angry."


translate English day9_hk_ea40b519:


    sc "If you don't like it, then don't make me mad."


translate English day9_hk_4cbb5577:


    nar "Without looking back at her, I kneel down on the floor and take out the first-aid kit from underneath the chair."


translate English day9_hk_9ad0da32:


    nar "I brought this here knowing it would probably come in handy at least once."


translate English day9_hk_bd115079:


    nar "Which is why it's more important than ever to be wary of outsiders."


translate English day9_hk_ca45c453:


    sc "I need to take care of that, so strip."


translate English day9_hk_a356f1e6:


    hk_b "Now? {w}Seriously?!"


translate English day9_hk_82ef0886:


    sc "No one can see you, so what's the big deal?"


translate English day9_hk_14a6f571:


    hk_b "I guess so... {w}You're right... You're always taking care of me."


translate English day9_hk_6ebea7e8:


    nar "She goes to remove the leather belt around her waist before stopping awkwardly."


translate English day9_hk_bd488590:


    nar "I look at her quizzically my head cocked to one side. {w}I wasn't trying to imitate her, but I can hear the sound of bones cracking in my stiff neck."


translate English day9_hk_f3856458:


    hk_b "...I d-don't know how to get it off."


translate English day9_hk_0ffbffc4:


    sc "Sigh... Even though I explain it to you every morning?"


translate English day9_hk_8532a442:


    hk_b "Well, what do you expect? I, and I mean that in the truest sense possible, don't usually wear frilly clothes like this."


translate English day9_hk_83cf311c:



    nvl clear
    "\n I have no choice but to get behind her, trying to feel out the zipper that runs down the back. Just like always."


translate English day9_hk_4d87a6b9:


    et "Like how every morning I faithfully help the bishop to get ready. {w}I remove her thick jacket, undo the buttons on her shirt, and tie her long, white hair into a ponytail so it doesn't get in the way."


translate English day9_hk_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_hk_ea6a946b:


    "\n It's not easy working in the Cleanup Department with long hair. Usually, the length of one's hair and the state in which it's in reveals how much that person cares about themself, but the truth is none of that means anything to her."


translate English day9_hk_0e7a4c65:


    "I cut my hair and the symbolism that goes along with it at the same time. {w}As someone whose only real interest is money, it was easier for me to cut it all off before I developed any real attachment to it."


translate English day9_hk_056ce37a:


    "Meanwhile, her focus is solely on keeping her beautiful hair the way it is. So that when other people see it, they'll make the assumption that she loves herself."


translate English day9_hk_be111716:


    et "Once I remove her shirt, her white back springs into view. {w}As do the countless scars that cover it."


translate English day9_hk_e7c1cbf7:



    nvl clear
    "\n She doesn't shiver, despite the cold night air. And she doesn't flinch even as I apply the disinfectant directly to her still-bleeding wound. {w}The only thing shaking is my own hand."


translate English day9_hk_773d39cb:


    et "In spite of who she is, Haku still tends to attract a lot of interest and gossip. {w}Probably due to how strongly she stands out."


translate English day9_hk_7de6d455:



    nvl clear
    "\n Her vividly defined vertebrae and shoulder blades, her pure white skin... she's gorgeous. {w}It's pointless to even try and put beauty of her magnitude into words."


translate English day9_hk_c84cea1c:


    "The first time I laid eyes on her, I was taken aback, wondering how someone that beautiful could exist in this world. {w}She seemed unreal."


translate English day9_hk_452b8a55:


    "It seems almost like a waste for someone as beautiful as her with such a laid-back yet always courteous attitude and to be in charge of a garbage dump that goes by the unassumingly upright name of the Cleanup Department."


translate English day9_hk_31b6944a:


    et "I know she does it in order to hide her scars, though I have no idea how long she's had them for."


translate English day9_hk_85a8876e:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Your hands aren't too cold, which is nice.\""


translate English day9_hk_ba3b0456:


    "\"Mine? I beg to differ.\""


translate English day9_hk_e4bec118:


    "\"At the very least they feel warm against my skin.\""


translate English day9_hk_c306f494:


    et "\"They're a normal temperature, just like my body.\" {w}You're the one who's cold, I add belatedly, not wanting to come off as rude."


translate English day9_hk_d9df5f3f:


    "\n My body is warm, though it changes fairly quickly depending on the outside temperature."


translate English day9_hk_1d868152:


    "She's... incredibly pale."


translate English day9_hk_0e3fe93a:


    et "Despite being bundled up in her clothes, she's always as cold as marble. And although I know she dislikes the cold, there are times where it almost seems like the opposite."


translate English day9_hk_26384302:


    sc "How did you get hurt anyway?"


translate English day9_hk_43718abb:


    hk_b "Oh. Before I came here, I stopped by the Academics Department to get a report on the Pestis Field from Kashiko."


translate English day9_hk_f42c8063:


    hk_b "She gave me an amulet that she said was a gift from the Academics bishop."


translate English day9_hk_ae9fac86:


    hk_b "All of which was well and good, but I completely forgot to bring it with me."


translate English day9_hk_59ad81b8:


    sc "You forgot?"


translate English day9_hk_d2ef2941:


    hk_b "It would've been a pain in the butt to go all the way back."


translate English day9_hk_c53876e7:


    sc "A pain in the butt, huh?"


translate English day9_hk_1ffde6ea:


    hk_b "So I went into the woods like usual..."


translate English day9_hk_35eb0a33:


    sc "You went into the woods, and...?"


translate English day9_hk_879ea972:


    hk_b "Hey, hey, hey! Do you really need to repeat back everything I say?" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_1f7ac762:


    hk_b "I accidentally attracted the attention of some nearby Lost, beat them 16 to 1, and... here I am."


translate English day9_hk_aed7e67b:


    hk_b "Whew! One more tale to add to the saga,"


translate English day9_hk_0642a5b2:


    extend " am I right..."


translate English day9_hk_132ffb68:


    sc "That's one thing about you I really hate."


translate English day9_hk_aa70fd0a:


    hk_b "You really hate it, huh?"


translate English day9_hk_4ff99959:


    sc "Yes! I can't stand it, in fact! {w}Why can't you ever call me to help you?"


translate English day9_hk_abfcd42a:


    sc "You're the one always saying that a bishop, but especially someone like you, shouldn't go walking around outside by themself."


translate English day9_hk_f588f8ea:


    hk_b "I know, I know. I get it, trust me. {w}I'll make sure to call you next time. Is that better?"


translate English day9_hk_8efcb970:


    sc "You know the other bishops do that without being told to."


translate English day9_hk_d3a72205:


    hk_b "Stop throwing a hissy fit. And yes, that's an order."


translate English day9_hk_8e2adc8e:


    sc "You never listen to anyone but yourself!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_54bea41b:


    hk_b "Stop being so cranky already! I mean it!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_8863ee17:


    nar "Even with the scars, I think Haku has the most purest body of anyone around."


translate English day9_hk_2ac71d8e:


    nar "It's because she's a person uninfected by Pestis, a body devoid of divine power through the total lack of even one stigmata."


translate English day9_hk_de669814:


    nar "There are rare cases where stigmata don't appear on a person's body after the age of seven."


translate English day9_hk_f833ade5:


    nar "Those without divine power usually die young, as they cannot resist the effects of Pestis."


translate English day9_hk_7e788f03:


    nar "Which is one of the ways in which I come in handy, so to speak. {w}I can see the Pestis Field and warn her."


translate English day9_hk_15ef4382:


    nar "At least she's alive. Her body was perfected while missing this integral piece, and she was still gifted the position of bishop even with her inadequate form."


translate English day9_hk_85fe040f:


    nar "I stay by her side and keep a watchful eye out for her own protection. I feel confident that her wound is a manifestation of stigmata."


translate English day9_hk_0993f2d4:


    sc "Okay, all done." with sshake


translate English day9_hk_d19389cf:


    hk_b "Ow!!! {w}Is that how you're supposed to treat a patient?"


translate English day9_hk_43d5bbad:


    sc "If you feel capable of babbling bizarre nonsense, then you'll probably live. {w}But you need to rest for the time being, Haku..."


translate English day9_hk_a6fc86a1:


    hk_b "..."


translate English day9_hk_57960a33:


    nar "There's no answer. I take that to mean she has no complaints."


translate English day9_hk_6031d4f2:


    sc "Do you usually receive such gifts from the bishop of the Academics Department?"


translate English day9_hk_13fb1a6e:


    hk_b "Hrm? Yeah. She likes doing that sort of thing."


translate English day9_hk_7c41d547:


    hk_b "Even when I was a young girl, she'd often give me a doll or a book before wandering off."


translate English day9_hk_6f73d8dc:


    hk_b "It's not that I dislike her per se, but I don't really enjoy her company."


translate English day9_hk_86c8bc00:


    nar "Evelynn Violetta."


translate English day9_hk_3f78703a:


    nar "She acted as the auxiliary bishop when Haku's father was still the bishop of the Academics Department,"


translate English day9_hk_907aa5ab:


    nar "and watched over young Haku while she grew up within the temple walls as a nanny of sorts."


translate English day9_hk_aef5dd75:


    nar "Haku loves nothing more than to reminiscence on her past, including heroic tales of bravery, and yet she doesn't really seem to like to talk about that lady at all."


translate English day9_hk_8b96f2bd:


    nar "Which is why the only thing I know is that young Haku was basically bored with her apparent indifference."


translate English day9_hk_c37f4767:


    hk_b "Have you ever talked to her?"


translate English day9_hk_0d4a7d8d:


    sc "Not really, no."


translate English day9_hk_e11a8576:


    hk_b "Evelynn considers herself the manifestation of femininity."


translate English day9_hk_9d3004c0:


    hk_b "That as long as you are born a woman, you will have the same shared existence as every other woman alive."


translate English day9_hk_2b60ec98:


    hk_b "All I'm saying is, when the time comes for you to stand before her as a woman, you better be careful."


translate English day9_hk_e769b697:


    nar "I'm the only other person here, and yet she speaks in a hushed voice, as if afraid of being overheard."


translate English day9_hk_f6bfaf4b:


    sc "Didn't she give you some kind of incense before?"


translate English day9_hk_fce7eb46:


    hk_b "Yes... She was concerned that I wasn't getting sufficient sleep at night."


translate English day9_hk_c3d863a8:


    hk_b "Though I'm not sure how the hell she'd know about my sleep problems when I never mentioned it even once."


translate English day9_hk_38dba58e:


    sc "Still, it was nice of her to care about you like that."


translate English day9_hk_df4544d9:


    hk_b "I know that. I mean it. But... {w}I don't know. It's complicated..."


translate English day9_hk_76dbc06f:


    sc "Well then... Did you run into anyone at the temple today other than Ravi?"


translate English day9_hk_fab8d475:


    hk_b "Hrm... Just Dr. Grette, I guess."


translate English day9_hk_3d80b250:


    sc "That must have been nice. What did you talk about?"


translate English day9_hk_5906e2ca:


    hk_b "Just... work."


translate English day9_hk_99778717:


    nar "I can't see her expression since I'm zipping her back up,"


translate English day9_hk_356a5117:


    nar "but I can tell something's wrong by her somewhat lackluster tone of voice."


translate English day9_hk_d9c77c29:


    nar "She's normally overjoyed at just the mention of Auxiliary Bishop Grette's name alone, so her subdued reaction is unusual."


translate English day9_hk_00a0a202:


    hk_b "Who did you see?"


translate English day9_hk_79d4a5ee:


    sc "Hrm... I basically just worked. It's not like I had more to do than usual, and yet the day seemed to drag on without end..."


translate English day9_hk_e1bd64c9:


    hk_b "Sounds like you were bored. You shouldn't be zoning out while busy with work."


translate English day9_hk_ee9e856c:


    hk_b "Knowing you, I bet your thoughts were full of department related worries."


translate English day9_hk_5121c9b7:


    sc "I wouldn't have to worry if the bishop did their job properly."


translate English day9_hk_d956b0d4:


    nar "I blurt out before immediately slapping my hand over my mouth in shock of what I just said."


translate English day9_hk_ba93c70a:


    nar "Haku laughs in response, seemingly more amused than annoyed."


translate English day9_hk_e1f6d598:


    hk_b "How about instead of turning to the incompetent bishop, we ask the auxiliary bishop what exactly is bothering her?"


translate English day9_hk_57b50c5e:


    nar "Not this again... She knows exactly what's wrong, but the way she so straightforwardly asks me to tell her is somewhat unnerving."


translate English day9_hk_1857a0ea:


    nar "Is something bothering me?"


translate English day9_hk_a0985180:


    sc "To be honest, I'm worried about the new recruits."


translate English day9_hk_2bd21a51:


    hk_b "Oh yeah?"


translate English day9_hk_9fd29709:


    sc "There's just... so much they don't know."


translate English day9_hk_ddbf9a6a:


    sc "If I don't do something, I worry we'll end up with an unfortunate repeat performance of what happened last time, and yet [na] refuses to listen to me."


translate English day9_hk_e1898aab:


    sc "And Maya... she's currently avoiding me. {w}Despite still having no idea what she's doing..."


translate English day9_hk_8ac7e427:


    hk_b "I figured as much. You've gone above and beyond looking out for them."


translate English day9_hk_20d286a7:


    sc "It's not just them. I've actually been thinking about this for a while now. {w}Temple life is rough--the Disposal Squad even more so..."


translate English day9_hk_78a25c2f:


    sc "I was lucky enough to get used to the routine fairly quickly, but things quickly spiral out of control when kids are dumped into the department completely unaware and uneducated."


translate English day9_hk_a39f21a2:


    sc "Watching as people lose their minds and die a horrible death is not necessarily my idea of a good time..."


translate English day9_hk_592af97c:


    sc "...Though I have no idea what it's like from your vantage point."


translate English day9_hk_3a660a33:


    hk_b "No, you do you have a point. {w}I used to feel the same way as you once upon a time."


translate English day9_hk_546b0651:


    nar "I look up at her. The smile she had on her face earlier is gone, replaced by a more somber expression."


translate English day9_hk_e6166c55:


    hk_b "I've always said that the moment you step foot in the Underworld, your life is as good as over..."


translate English day9_hk_8b98a5f7:


    hk_b "...and yet I can't bring myself to simply abandon anyone who I can tell has managed to retain even the faintest glimmer of life in their souls."


translate English day9_hk_c3f271e6:


    hk_b "If you stumble on a person waiting for salvation, praying desperately to a God who may or may not even be listening for help,"


translate English day9_hk_8ea33817:


    hk_b "someone has to hear them, right? {w}If not God himself, then another person at least.."


translate English day9_hk_669bb0bf:


    nar "..."


translate English day9_hk_c6461680:


    hk_b "And yet everyone dies while imagining that moment when their dreams come true."


translate English day9_hk_2dcdf8e9:


    hk_b "If it's this religion's policy that some people must be culled from the proverbial herd,"


translate English day9_hk_49e940f1:


    hk_b "then who are we to say otherwise?"


translate English day9_hk_354589c9:


    nar "She says, almost as if speaking to herself, before looking at me once more."


translate English day9_hk_064f5713:


    nar "Haku usually says these things in an attempt at cheering me up, but this time I get the impression she's trying to cheer herself up."


translate English day9_hk_c89a2ce6:


    sc "There's... actually nothing bothering me. Why did you think otherwise?"


translate English day9_hk_b74e6c6b:


    hk_b "There's not? {w}That's odd. I'd naturally assumed you were worried about those two."


translate English day9_hk_c3903b25:


    sc "I have been struggling with them for days, but I think it's time to be pragmatic about it."


translate English day9_hk_dd783f07:


    sc "You know how busy I am with my own work. I don't really want to waste any more time thinking about them."


translate English day9_hk_9fca7fe9:


    hk_b "You do seem pretty tired."


translate English day9_hk_3ec6c35c:


    sc "Are you happy now?"


translate English day9_hk_4ff2a4af:


    hk_b "Not exactly... I've been dealing with my own interpersonal problems recently. {w}Which is why I was hoping to get your perspective on the issue."


translate English day9_hk_97e6eec3:


    nar "Despite her words, it doesn't actually seem like she wants to talk about it. Kind of like me."


translate English day9_hk_42af82cd:


    nar "Though even if she doesn't want to talk about it, she probably seeks words of sympathy or even encouragement."


translate English day9_hk_bd8fe2ed:


    sc "Sometimes I get the feeling that you're not afraid of anything..."


translate English day9_hk_0b417aca:


    hk_b "Me? Ha ha ha... Quite the opposite. {w}You should know better than anyone."


translate English day9_hk_2a4b8608:


    nar "Her laughter sounds surprised almost. Of course I know different, despite my words. {w}And I also know exactly what she's afraid of."


translate English day9_hk_956c12d9:


    nar "I said what I did because I know she enjoys hearing it."


translate English day9_hk_e1e40fd9:


    hk_b "There's quite a lot I'm afraid of. {w}And I know very well what all those things are. Like the dark, for example..."


translate English day9_hk_96ab5f07:


    hk_b "Also dogs, and my father's orders."


translate English day9_hk_62d0bf65:


    sc "I really don't like that man... Even more so, knowing that you fear him as well. {w}He gives me the creeps."


translate English day9_hk_1cc91a0d:


    hk_b "You joke too much about other people's fathers."


translate English day9_hk_95b607b8:


    sc "I'm being serious. {w}If I were actually a man... Oh!"


translate English day9_hk_a6fc86a1_1:


    hk_b "..."


translate English day9_hk_77791284:


    sc "..."


translate English day9_hk_1a94fda5:


    hk_b "Pfft! Go on! If you were a man? {w}What would you do? {w}Hrm?" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_86fa4e48:


    hk_b "Ha ha ha! Going off on that again? You really must be sick! {w}Ha ha ha!"


translate English day9_hk_48f333d7:


    nar "Fuck, that's not what I meant... {w}It's just one verbal gaffe after another tonight. And all in front of Haku, no less!"


translate English day9_hk_7711234d:


    hk_b "Heh heh heh... Now see here. Unlike me, you're the one who actually has no idea what they're afraid of."


translate English day9_hk_76d09660:


    hk_b "I'm not saying you're an idiot or anything... {w}And I don't think you're completely unaware. {w}On the contrary, you're kind of a coward."


translate English day9_hk_ade19daa:


    nar "I simply stare at her, not really wanting to pursue this topic any deeper. I have no desire to hear what she thinks my weaknesses are."


translate English day9_hk_adb5ee6a:


    sc "For what it's worth, I don't think I'm afraid of anything in particular. {w}When you're prepared to die at any moment, then what's left to fear?"


translate English day9_hk_dc6ddb56:


    sc "That's simply how it goes. {w}Those who are afraid have yet to make their peace with their own mortality."


translate English day9_hk_70bb70fd:


    hk_b "I disagree. {w}It's not that you don't fear death, but more that you have no regrets or remorse for the life you've lived."


translate English day9_hk_bf4d2cf1:


    hk_b "Which is the state you're currently in. It's honestly no different from being dead already."


translate English day9_hk_e52a4fff:


    hk_b "I'm not saying you're actually dead, though. {w}Because, unlike a corpse, you're constantly in a heightened state of anxiety."


translate English day9_hk_feaf657f:


    hk_b "Like you are right now... and yesterday... and the day before that..."


translate English day9_hk_5e43c4ba:


    nar "She stares off into space, seemingly in a much better mood than before."


translate English day9_hk_3feadbde:


    nar "Though I can't help but feel uneasy when she looks like that."


translate English day9_hk_3685b379:


    hk_b "You claim to not fear death, but how can you be so sure?"


translate English day9_hk_0027930a:


    sc "You're joking... right, Haku? As a priest on the Disposal Squad, my life is in constant peril."


translate English day9_hk_86da155e:


    hk_b "And yet, somehow, you're still here, alive and well. {w}You have no desire to taste death even once?"


translate English day9_hk_8d884508:


    sc "Huh?"


translate English day9_hk_3861eeb9:


    hk_b "I can give it to you."


translate English day9_hk_4cd548c6:


    nar "Her laughter seems to directly contrast the gravity of her words and she pulls out a knife."


translate English day9_hk_a9d122ff:


    nar "That knife... {w}I immediately recognize it,"


translate English day9_hk_d8045247:


    nar "and yet I find myself simply standing there, dumbfounded, acting as if I have no idea how she intends to use it."


translate English day9_hk_cfb22e33:


    hk_b "Now don't move."


translate English day9_hk_af3ac453:


    nar "She murmurs quietly as she places the blade against my neck. My exhausted stomach tightens in response."


translate English day9_hk_e8e7b676:


    nar "The blade feels cold. {w}Her voice, as emotionless as if she's talking to a person bound for execution, seems to match it, instinctively reminding me of death itself."


translate English day9_hk_26fa4e93:


    nar "I know there's no need to be afraid. The situation I suddenly find myself in is so ridiculous, that there's no need to panic."


translate English day9_hk_e1ca1b89:


    sc "...!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_1d33e681:


    nar "And yet, I find myself taking a step back. {w}My heart begins pounding in my chest once more, and I realize I'm holding my breath."


translate English day9_hk_0d392902:


    nar "I force myself to exhale, and Haku nonchalantly presses the blade against my skin."


translate English day9_hk_d952e568:


    sc "Haku! You're taking this joke way too far!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_fbc64075:


    hk_b "If you know I'm joking, then why are you so upset?"


translate English day9_hk_c815e23b:


    hk_b "You know full well I only carry this knife around for peeling fruit! {w}Not *people*."


translate English day9_hk_ca6aa50a:


    nar "She's right. I know the knife's blade is nowhere near sharp enough to cut off a human head."


translate English day9_hk_e09e51cd:


    nar "I knew she was simply amusing herself with her usual games, and I also knew that I had been in no real danger of dying."


translate English day9_hk_64c707ea:


    nar "And yet, I find, and found, myself shutting my eyes as tightly as possibly."


translate English day9_hk_55be9ac2:


    sc "What the hell do you want?"


translate English day9_hk_22bd9104:


    hk_b "I don't want you to be culled from the herd."


translate English day9_hk_1cfafedd:


    hk_b "They say there's no qualifications needed to dream, and yet in order to make those dreams a reality, it's imperative that one knows their own weaknesses."


translate English day9_hk_afadef20:


    hk_b "If you are unable to overcome them, you'll be cast-off from the group, just like the current new recruits and the ones who came before them..."


translate English day9_hk_7011591a:


    hk_b "You're the type who tends to see the bad in everything, and yet you have a habit of intentionally ignoring those faults of yours that deserve the most attention."


translate English day9_hk_a8da7d9b:


    sc "What's your point? {w}It's all so much easier when you only worry about your own role in the temple."


translate English day9_hk_337a7262:


    sc "Who has time for work when they're too busy dealing with trivial and irreversible problems?"


translate English day9_hk_cfc3ae12:


    sc "I have a lot to do tomorrow. {w}I gotta head back."


translate English day9_hk_7fae7f2b:


    nar "I practically jump to my feat. My heart which was startled into a state of panic, is still pounding away."


translate English day9_hk_768c010a:


    hk_b "You'll be here tomorrow, right? I would really like it if you did."


translate English day9_hk_e239e9a6:


    sc "No need to worry, Haku... {w}I'm not actually angry, so I have no reason not to come."


translate English day9_hk_ec9032ce:


    nar "Not wanting to see her smile, I leave the chapel without looking back."


translate English day9_hk_3d4da36e:


    nar "Her teasing smile is not the same as what a boss might show to their subordinate."


translate English day9_hk_811133bb:


    nar "Which only confuses me more."


translate English day9_hk_a1369eff:


    nar "Feeling as if you mean something to someone else is nothing more than selfish imposition on your part."


translate English day9_hk_316111c0:


    nar "Everyone needs a role to be filled in their life, and when the person who fills that role vanishes, they simply find a new body to take their place."


translate English day9_hk_4e5c0e9f:


    nar "That's what I tell myself as I pray for my pounding heart to quiet down."


translate English day9_hk_M_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_hk_M_00aa15fa:


    sc "...?"


translate English day9_hk_M_d248c364:


    nar "When I arrive at the entrance to the dorms, I see a shadow from across the hall. {w}It simply stands there, not moving."


translate English day9_hk_M_b10aa8da:


    sc "Maya?"


translate English day9_hk_M_bf73843b:


    nar "The face is one I know well. {w}She seems happy to see me on the surface, and yet her expression reveals a mix of emotions."


translate English day9_hk_M_81d9aa95:


    my "You're back earlier than I was expecting, Cue. {w}It's just... You weren't in your room, so... I figured you must have gone out somewhere."


translate English day9_hk_M_081b9a0c:


    my "It's been a while since I've seen you. {w}Well, I mean, we see each other every morning... but I guess I meant being able to talk like this..."


translate English day9_hk_M_bdbdba40:


    sc "Is there something you need to tell me?"


translate English day9_hk_M_d0b2408f:


    nar "I cut to the chase because I get the feeling that's what she wants me to do."


translate English day9_hk_M_2e778584:


    my "Actually... I was just curious why you two were fighting..."


translate English day9_hk_M_c3fbc7f5:


    my "I know that [na2] doesn't mean you any harm. {w}He just gets really angry sometimes..."


translate English day9_hk_M_e8f16c47:


    my "I guess you could say he's gone past the point of no return. Wh-What I mean is..."


translate English day9_hk_M_a6951fb5:


    my "I thought that maybe if you apologized to him again, the two of you might be able to be make up and get along..."


translate English day9_hk_M_77791284:


    sc "..."


translate English day9_hk_M_ab7a69d4:


    my "Oh... Don't get the wrong idea! I'm not saying that you're the only one at fault here, Cue."


translate English day9_hk_M_de6a17e0:


    my "But I'm sure that [na2] would apologize as well if you go first!"


translate English day9_hk_M_1e6a1cc0:


    sc "I'm sorry, Maya. But it's too late for apologies."


translate English day9_hk_M_3334fc23:


    my "..."


translate English day9_hk_M_94e7a65c:


    sc "Though I do owe you one, and have owed you one for a while."


translate English day9_hk_M_37be4f91:


    sc "I know you're probably disappointed in me, and I hate that you got caught up in this mess. {w}I'm sorry."


translate English day9_hk_M_6a9de352:


    sc "But I won't apologize to him."


translate English day9_hk_M_1665d0bd:


    my "B-But why...?"


translate English day9_hk_M_2780cf94:


    sc "Simply because there's no need to do so. I understand how you feel, but we've gone past the point of apologies."


translate English day9_hk_M_1379634f:


    sc "There's nothing I can do to fix things."


translate English day9_hk_M_0310d172:


    my "Then what about me?"


translate English day9_hk_M_9a6638fd:


    nar "The moment I saw her face, I knew I couldn't hide the truth from her any longer."


translate English day9_hk_M_f37b17a2:


    nar "There's no coming back from this."


translate English day9_hk_M_1b60f3a1:


    my "Whatever sparked this fight between you two, it has nothing to do with me."


translate English day9_hk_M_e881198e:


    my "But do you know the extent to which he bullies me?"


translate English day9_hk_M_8f61521f:


    my "Do you truly understand the extent to which your constant fighting affects his mood?!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_M_77791284_1:


    sc "..."


translate English day9_hk_M_b0745bdc:


    my "I need you to... to think about me in this equation a little more..."


translate English day9_hk_M_4ddda3a2:


    my "You can't just pretend like you don't see me, like I'm not here! I know you feel bad for me, Securett!!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_M_eba19bd4:


    sc "...Go back to your room unless you want to be late tomorrow."


translate English day9_hk_M_3334fc23_1:


    my "..."


translate English day9_hk_M_6e687a76:


    nar "Unable to give her a different answer, I end the conversation and walk past her."


translate English day9_hk_M_d6808694:


    nar "All I want is to keep walking, but I can't help but immediately turn to look back."


translate English day9_hk_M_9c6eac8c:


    "{nw}" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_M_d7cdef46:


    nar "Maya leaps forward, crying out in a voice clouded with so much anger that it sounded unrecognizable."


translate English day9_hk_M_b4c5d353:


    nar "I can hear her sharp inhale and exhale through her tightly clenched teeth."


translate English day9_hk_M_32b9c58a:


    nar "Caught off guard, I grab her arms, only just barely restraining her as she flails her limbs wildly."


translate English day9_hk_M_55f6e7fd:


    nar "In that moment, I hear what sounds like something hard hit the floor."


translate English day9_hk_M_77791284_2:


    sc "..."


translate English day9_hk_M_3334fc23_2:


    my "..."


translate English day9_hk_M_a14c3072:


    my "You knew all along, didn't you...?"


translate English day9_hk_M_d54682ad:


    nar "She bows her head, but I know right away that she's crying."


translate English day9_hk_M_8f278e49:


    my "I know it, too... I know everything. {w}I've been watching you for a while now, Cue..."


translate English day9_hk_M_cfebc57c:


    my "I'm not that stupid! I know everything!!" with sshake


translate English day9_hk_M_078c201b:


    nar "She shoves me away and runs off down the dark hallway."


translate English day9_hk_M_77fbdd54:


    nar "I watch her go, worried she'll trip and fall due to the state she's in, before lowering my gaze. I immediately spot a sharp drill bit."


translate English day9_hk_M_82bae15f:


    nar "When Haku pressed that knife of hers against me, I felt a moment of regret."


translate English day9_hk_M_6d79867e:


    nar "That I kept [na] around for Haku's sake is an excuse so dumb sounding that there's no way it could be true."


translate English day9_hk_M_50838773:


    nar "The truth is, I honestly enjoyed spending time with him, and I didn't want him to transfer to the Magic Department."


translate English day9_hk_M_1effc3b0:


    nar "I was afraid we'd no longer get to spend time together and that he would no longer see me as his friend."


translate English day9_hk_M_946d1825:


    sc "I..."


translate English day9_hk_M_c7a76e56:


    nar "I knew that. {w}And when I hurt them, I was likewise hurting myself."


translate English day9_hk_M_0cafb7b8:


    nar "Haku told me I have to overcome my own weaknesses in order to make my dreams come true,"


translate English day9_hk_M_8ec9dec0:


    nar "but a part of me knows, deep down, that there is no way I can overcome my own cowardice..."


translate English day9_hk_M_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_hk_M_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_hk_69401f3a:


    nar "When I wake up, I'm in the infirmary."


translate English day10_hk_bb219ac8:


    nar "The last thing I remember is that dirty scene in the bathroom. {w}I need to clean it up before Haku gets back."


translate English day10_hk_9934dd93:


    nar "I look over to see [na] fast asleep. {w}I manage to keep from crying out in surprise when I notice he's holding a paring knife."


translate English day10_hk_896d225f:


    nar "Pain suddenly explodes in my stomach as I regain consciousness. I hesitantly touch it only to see blood on my fingers."


translate English day10_hk_86984ace:


    nar "I inhale sharply in response. I knew this would happen eventually, but I never thought that day would be today."


translate English day10_hk_d03381b0:


    nar "Still, this is no time to be afraid. And luckily for me, there are some clean priests robes folded up nearby."


translate English day10_hk_09d71f19:


    nar "I quickly take off the hospital gown before returning to my usual priestly appearance."


translate English day10_hk_246085c3:


    pl "Where do you think you're going?"


translate English day10_hk_4c357cae:


    sc "WHOA!!!" with sshake


translate English day10_hk_700f6271:


    nar "I'm unable to help but cry out this time."


translate English day10_hk_483a282e:


    nar "He's sitting on the bed, right next to me, his gaze unfocused as if he's still half-asleep."


translate English day10_hk_18bcf13c:


    sc "...To work."


translate English day10_hk_70fbca6e:


    nar "I try to keep things as short and simple as possible."


translate English day10_hk_d4e3cfa1:


    nar "He nods, as if in understanding. {w}I move closer to him."


translate English day10_hk_48f5da28:


    pl "You'll be dead before you know it."


translate English day10_hk_a5b8451e:


    sc "Not any time soon."


translate English day10_hk_aa4a92b1:


    nar "Only because I haven't yet been ordered to do so. {w}Though I keep my verbal answer short and sweet."


translate English day10_hk_75ee81b6:


    nar "Then, as if dealing with a corpse or a child, I place my hand over his eyes in order to close his eyelids. When they reopen, I simply repeat the process, pressing them back down."


translate English day10_hk_a231b6e0:


    nar "When he finally settles down, the room regains its usual silence."


translate English day10_hk_452ec6d2:


    nar "The bathroom has already been cleaned up."


translate English day10_hk_5d3a19b9:


    nar "Technically speaking, whoever did it simply rinsed off the floor with water, though I'm surprised by how effective that basic technique was."


translate English day10_hk_25e29f34:


    nar "Haku's still not back by the time I finish up cleaning out the tub. It's already past three."


translate English day10_hk_8d6bf91a:


    nar "Anxiety gnaws at me."


translate English day10_hk_519aa983:


    nar "Though it doesn't happen often, there are times where Haku ends up spending the entire night in the forest chapel. {w}And though it's a rare occurrence, it does inevitably happen from time to time."


translate English day10_hk_e44e9a01:


    nar "I climb the stairs and step out onto the dark floor. {w}This is the only place where light can't reach."


translate English day10_hk_6d48dd3f:


    nar "Haku doesn't like being alone in this dark, cold, cramped space."


translate English day10_hk_4c9b4789:


    nar "There's a row of chairs, and she's sitting on one of them."


translate English day10_hk_db8d64cb:


    nar "She's usually so talkative that the air she exudes in that moment is so bizarre and so quiet that it takes my breath away."


translate English day10_hk_12fb487c:


    sc "I was looking for you, Haku... Did something happen?"


translate English day10_hk_a6fc86a1:


    hk_b "..."


translate English day10_hk_71238844:


    nar "Suspicious at how unresponsive she is, I wave my hand in front of her face." with sshake


translate English day10_hk_604e8972:


    nar "Only her eyes shift in my direction before she suddenly reaches out and grabs my wrist."


translate English day10_hk_beb91727:


    hk_b "I should be the one asking you that. You reek of blood. {w}Are you hurt? Who did this to you?"


translate English day10_hk_cfecb23a:


    nar "I instinctively try to pull back, but suddenly stop. {w}I'll only attract more unwelcome attention to myself if I panic."


translate English day10_hk_03f9bdad:


    sc "It's just a scratch. It happens a lot when I'm working."


translate English day10_hk_a78b6cd6:


    hk_b "It doesn't look like just a scratch to me. You've also been absent from work for a while now, you know."


translate English day10_hk_d1999ea6:


    sc "Let me go."


translate English day10_hk_437f65ff:


    hk_b "Why are you lying to me? {w}You're going to have to try a little harder if you plan on fooling me."


translate English day10_hk_dc2f3f36:


    hk_b "Assuming you can't do that, then tell me the truth. {w}Who stabbed you and where are you hurt?"


translate English day10_hk_94c23bea:


    nar "Her somber blue eyes stare at me without blinking. {w}Her grip on my wrist tightens, making no effort at hiding her own arousal."


translate English day10_hk_44f0f574:


    nar "I eventually manage to twist myself free."


translate English day10_hk_e48eb1cf:


    sc "Stop! {w}What does it matter who did this to me or the extent of my injuries? As long as I can show up to work tomorrow and get the job done, that's all that matters, right?" with sshake


translate English day10_hk_28fba6a2:


    hk_b "What did you say? {w}You can't possibly be serious right now..."


translate English day10_hk_98b3ac7a:


    hk_b "You know what? Sigh... This isn't important..."


translate English day10_hk_74b1ae76:


    nar "For a moment, she sounds on the brink of rage before nodding in resignation."


translate English day10_hk_704b11ac:


    nar "My wrist still throbs from her tight grip."


translate English day10_hk_80af9586:


    nar "I sit down next to her while trying to gauge her emotions. She holds her forehead in one hand before slowly turning to look at me."


translate English day10_hk_00b56639:


    hk_b "You can't be his punching bag forever. In fact, it would do you some good to hit him for once. Because it is imperative you strike first."


translate English day10_hk_427b05dc:


    sc "Sure... Whatever you say."


translate English day10_hk_9aa8e686:


    nar "Regardless of how we got here, I'm just glad she gave up."


translate English day10_hk_646d2bbf:


    nar "There's no way I will let her get caught up in this fight between [na2] and I, nor my personal affairs."


translate English day10_hk_3ba4bd3e:


    sc "What's that perfume?"


translate English day10_hk_391116e5:


    hk_b "Violetta. It's my father's favorite flower, as it most resembles the love of his life."


translate English day10_hk_10f17f93:


    hk_b "The smell makes me nauseous."


translate English day10_hk_223022ed:


    nar "A glimpse of lingering regret in perfume sprayed so innocuously."


translate English day10_hk_ac432295:


    nar "Haku always wanted to be a woman."


translate English day10_hk_da248054:


    nar "\"The type of noble woman who is innocent and self-sacrificing, pure and calm, yet vulnerable in her ignorance.\" The type of woman her father adored most."


translate English day10_hk_128446d7:


    nar "The version of the bishop who existed in the daytime was comprised of a myriad collection of illusions she'd long since desired."


translate English day10_hk_2a5b3113:


    nar "Which is why I never wanted to meet her. {w}Who could possibly enjoy seeing the weak side of a person you admire and respect?"


translate English day10_hk_10628aec:


    hk_b "I like touching you, though I have no desire to go further..."


translate English day10_hk_f434d1fd:


    hk_b "The nightmares only made things worse, though never to the point of true terror."


translate English day10_hk_9983887f:


    nar "The words she suddenly speaks are so disjointed that it makes me wonder if she's drunk, exhausted, or possibly drugged."


translate English day10_hk_5a450530:


    sc "Haku, it's late. You should really go back to your room and get some rest."


translate English day10_hk_f635cb90:


    hk_b "Am I bothering you?"


translate English day10_hk_f0227fd7:


    nar "I shut my mouth and shake my head, not wanting that all too familiar dialogue to continue. {w}Thankfully, she closes her eyes without saying another word. She looks tired."


translate English day10_hk_6ccf782d:


    hk_b "I'm sorry... Please stay with me. That's... that's all I want right now. {w}You don't have to talk if you don't want to."


translate English day10_hk_e2aeead5:


    nar "As the heavy silence deepens between us, she suddenly reaches into her pocket as if having suddenly remembered something."


translate English day10_hk_b547519a:


    nar "Then she pulls out a small box."


translate English day10_hk_633f32f5:


    hk_b "A gift. Open it."


translate English day10_hk_9fba19fd:


    nar "Inside lays a brooch inlaid with golden amber."


translate English day10_hk_b2a5a597:


    nar "What a bold move. How dare she insist on giving something like this to me as a gift."


translate English day10_hk_786bb3ad:


    nar "Beneath the contoured brooch lays one of Haku's favorite tea leaves."


translate English day10_hk_d32be8c9:


    nar "It emits a faint smell that reminds me of her kind smile."


translate English day10_hk_005bc839:


    nar "When a gift is filled with love, I guess it's possible to envision the giver's face just by looking at it."


translate English day10_hk_5ed4bc9e:


    sc "Why are you giving me something like this? Do you not want it anymore?"


translate English day10_hk_75ced487:


    hk_b "You think I'm throwing it out? I told you, it's a gift. {w}I had a feeling you might not be in the best of moods today, and I was right. You need to take care of yourself."


translate English day10_hk_bcd6a9ea:


    nar "That's usually my line."


translate English day10_hk_01a3bda1:


    sc "You haven't talked to the bishop of the Health Department lately, have you?"


translate English day10_hk_169fd91e:


    hk_b "Yes... though only about work."


translate English day10_hk_43061640:


    nar "Grette is the only one who knows everything concerning both mine and Haku's situations."


translate English day10_hk_d1d41d47:


    nar "It's thanks to her help that I found a job here in the temple to begin with, and as for Haku, Grette is both her doctor and her first true love."


translate English day10_hk_f32ba313:


    nar "Before entering the academy, she had left the capital so Grette could take care of her in her own home. {w}To treat her for a mental illness."


translate English day10_hk_95406e6e:


    nar "It was thanks to Gregor Cornish, the current bishop of the Health Department, who made it all possible,"


translate English day10_hk_1911cf41:


    nar "and he also went out of his way to take the young girl under his guardianship in place of her father."


translate English day10_hk_496e4383:


    nar "Which is why Haku acts so much like a child when dealing with them."


translate English day10_hk_91daf9de:


    hk_b "It was given to me when I first got my position as bishop here... Hard to believe it's already been three years since then."


translate English day10_hk_44790721:


    hk_b "Evelynn had taken up handicrafts and was in the midst of her passion for doing so."


translate English day10_hk_d7d61fe8:


    hk_b "At the time, the work I had to deal with was a lot for me and, honestly speaking, contrary with my character... Still, the doctor and the other bishops, they... well..."


translate English day10_hk_716224f2:


    hk_b "They encouraged me, along with that old geezer, and so I continued to give it my best shot."


translate English day10_hk_ab3029e2:


    hk_b "After that, this thing helped me quite a bit by giving me something to focus my energy into."



translate English day10_hk_f8a74e9e:


    sc "So why are you giving it to me?"


translate English day10_hk_2a1484d7:


    hk_b "I have no place to put it."


translate English day10_hk_d42056c2:


    nar "I threw away my diary a few days ago, and now I'm tidying up my room."


translate English day10_hk_0a7a9c14:


    nar "I can't seem to figure out why she's getting rid of everything in her life that's helped make her the person she is today."


translate English day10_hk_04f8cb6c:


    sc "You don't need it anymore?"


translate English day10_hk_ed6e8ac0:


    hk_b "Ha ha... Maybe the reason why you're always getting hit is because you're always right."


translate English day10_hk_77791284:


    sc "..."


translate English day10_hk_876dc89f:


    hk_b "I've come to the realization that everything I've ever felt until now was nothing but an illusion. Or rather, the exact opposite of the truth."


translate English day10_hk_3d9fac2e:


    nar "I'm steadily growing frustrated. {w}I get the feeling something is happening inside of her."


translate English day10_hk_b0956f46:


    nar "That once the day is done, I'll never get another chance to speak with her again."


translate English day10_hk_50182dad:


    hk_b "Were you hoping for something a bit more expensive?"


translate English day10_hk_52043f19:


    sc "Of course not."


translate English day10_hk_a89d3c57:


    hk_b "So then why do you look so glum?"


translate English day10_hk_973744da:


    sc "I always look glum..."


translate English day10_hk_bd1ca49a:


    nar "As if annoyed by my answer, she reaches forward, squishing my face between both hands, and forces me to look her in the eyes."


translate English day10_hk_47e860d9:


    hk_b "The shadows that cloud your face have turned your eyes purple. There's not even a speck of the sun's brightness to be found."


translate English day10_hk_df9ab00c:


    hk_b "It's like you're running from the light, digging yourself as deep as you can to hide from it... {w}Honestly, it looks good on you."


translate English day10_hk_b2eb5c9e:


    sc "You reek of cigarette smoke..."


translate English day10_hk_b7267fd3:


    nar "I shake my head hard, escaping her grasp. I've rejected her advances twice at this point today."


translate English day10_hk_7f26a44e:


    nar "I know that she tends to act this way when she's depressed. Kind of like how normal people embrace dolls or animals."


translate English day10_hk_b491bf9f:


    nar "But why is she acting this way today?"


translate English day10_hk_eb5a9ff3:


    nar "I can tell by the look on her face that just because she doesn't seem angry doesn't mean everything's okay."


translate English day10_hk_d22081f2:


    nar "Unable to simply stand there and do nothing, I hold the hand I had just shoved away."


translate English day10_hk_c8bf17e2:


    hk_b "You're acting somewhat different than yesterday. Were you able to get your anger under control?"


translate English day10_hk_e78aa4e5:


    sc "I told you, I wasn't angry... Just scared. {w}It took a while for me to come to grips with the way I am."


translate English day10_hk_56632311:


    sc "That's why... I didn't want to acknowledge your words as the truth because I was afraid of getting hurt."


translate English day10_hk_361abeb3:


    hk_b "I'm glad to see you're finally beginning to feel a healthy amount of fear."


translate English day10_hk_6ee14d14:


    hk_b "Everyone sees a fearless state as being brave, when in reality it's nothing more than simple stupidity!"


translate English day10_hk_faa1bc92:


    hk_b "Now that you know what you're afraid of, you can overcome it."


translate English day10_hk_3fd74281:


    sc "So what happens to me if I lack the confidence to do so?"


translate English day10_hk_0328087a:


    hk_b "You get culled from the herd. {w}Just like I said yesterday."


translate English day10_hk_09a55498:


    nar "It's hard for me to believe I've reached the point where turning to her for advice or encouragement feels like the most obvious thing to do."


translate English day10_hk_4b043c2a:


    nar "I can't believe I was hurt by such egotistical greed."


translate English day10_hk_9336377c:


    nar "I nod weakly, my breathing shallow and trembling. {w}She begins a new topic, as if trying to show sympathy to my plight."


translate English day10_hk_214657c4:


    hk_b "You know, up until it happened, I had no idea I was crazy. {w}I figured it was all due to the effects of Pestis."


translate English day10_hk_0da62b77:


    hk_b "Do you have any idea how much that woman's knowledge helped me? Because all disease can be cured by the human hand."


translate English day10_hk_601a8af6:


    hk_b "I knew that someday, I would be cured, and my father would proudly acknowledge me as his daughter."


translate English day10_hk_f963b50b:


    hk_b "Those moments of positivity were always fleeting unfortunately. All children must experience their adolescence, just as you are now."


translate English day10_hk_77791284_1:


    sc "..."


translate English day10_hk_f9fc4b66:


    hk_b "Starting from the moment I realized nothing I believed in made sense, I became consumed with hatred."


translate English day10_hk_df8a26d7:


    hk_b "Hatred toward anyone who resembled my father, toward the troubling situation my beloved doctor was dealing with, toward the rumors that persistently followed me wherever I went, and even my own religion..."


translate English day10_hk_99e400df:


    hk_b "I became so sick and tired of it all that I fled the doctor's house and began sleeping around with anyone who seemed even remotely inclined, regardless of gender."


translate English day10_hk_6c52d5b7:


    hk_b "I was constantly in a state of such intoxication that I don't remember much,"


translate English day10_hk_1641f755:


    hk_b "but whenever things got really rough, I'd always call Greg up. That's the only thing I do remember."


translate English day10_hk_6c625d58:


    hk_b "Then, whether it early in the morning or he was busy with work, he'd come running to my side to calm me down and provide comfort..."


translate English day10_hk_e1506cfd:


    hk_b "Ha! I wonder why he did that for me."


translate English day10_hk_e35a5d17:


    hk_b "Why was he always so kind to me? To a woman like me?"


translate English day10_hk_7bb63ca7:


    nar "She buries her face in her hands. I can hear her voice trembling as she fights to hold back tears."


translate English day10_hk_5281468f:


    nar "Just as I'm about to reach over to comfort her, she suddenly looks up at me, her eyes open wide. {w}It's an expression that shows not even the slightest hint of sadness."


translate English day10_hk_f42db969:


    hk_b "But we can't keep dwelling on the past forever now, can we?"


translate English day10_hk_be62e5f0:


    nar "She speaks in a honest and cheerful sounding voice."


translate English day10_hk_b71f3312:


    nar "She's always been a person of extreme mood swings, though today more than usual..."


translate English day10_hk_dd7d32c1:


    sc "Haku, tell me what's really going on. {w}Did the Cardinal say something to you?"


translate English day10_hk_1b0d615f:


    hk_b "You should be ashamed, Securett. Someone who ranks that far above you deserves the respectful honorific Sir!"


translate English day10_hk_b67a4942:


    sc "I'm sorry, but there's no way I can show that man any kind of respect. {w}A man is more than their title and name."


translate English day10_hk_9de95e96:


    hk_b "Be that as it may, if the world needs him, then who are we to say otherwise?"


translate English day10_hk_93e786ac:


    hk_b "Considering my own petty feelings and the decisions I've made that have only wrecked havoc in the world, I should be the one to abandon everything I've done and conform to the majority. Don't you agree?"


translate English day10_hk_44a5b217:


    sc "What the hell are you talking about? {w}Are you being serious?"


translate English day10_hk_05c1de95:


    sc "You've changed... You didn't start acting like this until a few days ago."


translate English day10_hk_80584996:


    sc "No matter how much religion and hierarchy are forced upon us in the capital,"


translate English day10_hk_ff315198:


    sc "you remained the only righteous person who stood strong in their beliefs."


translate English day10_hk_26f0505b:


    nar "My voice begins to tremble as I speak."


translate English day10_hk_c545a2a0:


    nar "I would have stopped speaking if she'd made any move to argue on her behalf, but she seems indifferent."


translate English day10_hk_d742efd1:


    nar "This person before me isn't the Haku I know."


translate English day10_hk_21b7a35e:


    sc "You've been acting really weird lately... {w}And then yesterday... and today as well. Why didn't you call me in for work?"


translate English day10_hk_62c8f5f0:


    sc "As the auxiliary bishop, it's my obligation to protect you."


translate English day10_hk_71b61045:


    sc "But lately it almost feels like you're running away from happiness. {w}I don't understand what prompted this change?"


translate English day10_hk_136b0eba:


    hk_b "You think I changed? {w}If that's how you feel, then clearly you never knew me to begin with."


translate English day10_hk_c06e78c1:


    hk_b "The only person who's changed around here is *you*. For a while now, in truth. {w}You've become hollow."


translate English day10_hk_ad950bd1:


    hk_b "That you were so prepared to give everything for me was only possible because, even from the very beginning, nothing meant anything to you."


translate English day10_hk_2aa90455:


    nar "There's nothing I can say in response to that."


translate English day10_hk_8409f743:


    nar "She might speak fast, but her pronunciation is precise enough that even an idiot like me can understand her."


translate English day10_hk_19ceca56:


    hk_b "If you had anything of value in your life, like a friend or any connection to another human being,"


translate English day10_hk_17eafd94:


    hk_b "I wonder if it would have still been so easy for you to give up everything for me."


translate English day10_hk_2f750b2c:


    nar "I stand there, frozen, but as always, she offers me a choice. {w}Though both paths are long and dark."


translate English day10_hk_3b4cec2d:


    nar "The thought of walking that road alone makes me feel like I'm suffocating. Which path do I choose?"


translate English day10_hk_9834e51b:


    sc "I can do it. {w}For you, right now..."


translate English day10_hk_9bbca08b:


    hk_b "Sigh."


translate English day10_hk_c1f9f202:


    nar "Far beyond the ability to think straight, the words fall from my lips in short bursts. Haku closes her eyes and laughs, her exhale sounding so much like a sigh."


translate English day10_hk_8c260d9b:


    nar "I would be overjoyed if that smile meant she was satisfied with my response."


translate English day10_hk_b575b2a4:


    hk_b "Now that you've lost it, so to speak, you can finally do it."


translate English day10_hk_d893d531:


    sc "Haku, I..."


translate English day10_hk_f8710daf:


    hk_b "Don't get the wrong idea. {w}I'm not trying to say that's a bad thing. I'm happy you've made it to this point."


translate English day10_hk_68bb978d:


    hk_b "With that said... Why do you lie to yourself and continue trying to lie to me?"


translate English day10_hk_f0eee873:


    sc "I'm not lying to you!" with sshake


translate English day10_hk_e88e32c2:


    hk_b "Then why are you currently being chewed out in the middle of the night? It's almost as if you've become a sinner."


translate English day10_hk_d25d050b:


    hk_b "I told you before to stop doing that."


translate English day10_hk_77791284_2:


    sc "..."


translate English day10_hk_fcd96c24:


    hk_b "Sigh... It's fine. {w}You've always been slow on the uptake."


translate English day10_hk_2e55e2a2:


    sc "I don't think I can do that... {w}I know too much already. Far too much..."


translate English day10_hk_6da98438:


    nar "I can't deny her words any longer. A part of me suspects this is the way she's always wanted me to be."


translate English day10_hk_036a0b52:


    nar "Well aware of my own humanity and free will."


translate English day10_hk_04e66d3c:


    nar "And now that I am concious of it, I have no choice but to accept it."


translate English day10_hk_0f2e955b:


    sc "It felt different when it was you and I alone, locked up in that cage."


translate English day10_hk_295fd1bf:


    sc "I became scared of so many things."


translate English day10_hk_214a7a64:


    sc "I still am, Haku... {w}I may not be afraid of death, but I am afraid of never seeing you again..."


translate English day10_hk_48e78f7d:


    hk_b "Don't get the wrong idea, Securett. {w}I'm not trying to say that's a bad thing."


translate English day10_hk_0980b18d:


    hk_b "Rather, I'm glad you've finally come to think that way. {w}But it seems our paths must diverge moving forward."


translate English day10_hk_1bade8b5:


    hk_b "With that said, if you take even step off from the path you've chosen,"


translate English day10_hk_9fb03ec6:


    hk_b "that's the moment when we'll become strangers who will never see each other for the rest of their lives."


translate English day10_hk_a875ccb4:


    nar "I know exactly what she's trying to say. {w}She wants her independence."


translate English day10_hk_88d1d95e:


    nar "It's unclear whether it's from me or herself."


translate English day10_hk_a9a623d3:


    nar "But it's clear she wants to move forward alone."


translate English day10_hk_14f0de21:


    sc "I hate myself..."


translate English day10_hk_ba1968e4:


    nar "On the other hand, I love the facade I've crafted. {w}I would drown in it forever if that was possible."


translate English day10_hk_b3488c40:


    nar "Haku smiles and pats me on the shoulder, as if understanding exactly how I feel."


translate English day10_hk_75389b6c:


    hk_b "Perpetrating a lie forever is not the way to live. {w}We have to move forward as our true selves. Right?"


translate English day10_hk_bd6b2a15:


    nar "And then her face reverts to its original expression."


translate English day10_hk_539ee610:


    nar "Her expression appears serene, but it's not. More like unremarkable. {w}Up until now, I've never seen her look anywhere close to unremarkable."


translate English day10_hk_15eb0d7a:


    nar "Her words were not meant to hurt me, only state the facts."


translate English day10_hk_773bd39f:


    hk_b "I don't care if you use me as an excuse to protect yourself, but I advise against becoming dependent on doing so."


translate English day10_hk_43b9f5dd:


    hk_b "That is not the right way."


translate English day10_hk_77791284_3:


    sc "..."


translate English day10_hk_13eb93a8:


    hk_b "Also, I didn't ask you to help with work because I didn't need you. {w}It's not that deep."


translate English day10_hk_d8bd14e0:


    hk_b "You might be able to see the Pestis field, but your weaknesses severely outweights what strengths you have."


translate English day10_hk_a0a265c0:


    hk_b "I can make more progress by simply asking another priest to help or handling it on my own."


translate English day10_hk_c16f544b:


    nar "That's why I'm not hurt by her words. All she's doing is speaking the obvious truth."


translate English day10_hk_2fa9328a:


    sc "Understood."


translate English day10_hk_63e6db5c:


    nar "I answer with one simple word. {w}She turns to look at me while speaking somewhat ironically."


translate English day10_hk_b645a552:


    hk_b "Still not crying, huh? {w}Well, I figured as much."


translate English day10_hk_7977dc65:


    nar "She's still holding my hand, and I shake my head, not wanting her to let go."


translate English day10_hk_29d1a388:


    nar "She does, however, her expression remaining steadfast."


translate English day10_hk_8ba357ef:


    nar "There had been no warmth in her hand, and yet the moment it leaves mine, a chill sweeps through me."


translate English day10_hk_53477c95:


    hk_b "To tell you the truth, I'm not sure teaching you how to live when you were so empty to begin with was the right thing to do."


translate English day10_hk_445e89b6:


    hk_b "I don't get it at all."


translate English day10_hk_112bfaad:


    hk_b "The more I yearned for you, the slower and stupider I became. You in turn only grew weaker and cowardly."


translate English day10_hk_a7cd9012:


    hk_b "Maybe humans are simply beings that are unable to form mutual connections with each other."


translate English day10_hk_669bb0bf:


    nar "..."


translate English day10_hk_dfc99670:


    hk_b "I will say that I did truly enjoy the conversations we shared. {w}But there's no mistake... I regret ever having met you."


translate English day10_hk_9f856884:


    nar "Of all the days I've spent alive, today is definitely the most unfortunate."


translate English day10_hk_2dfcbd95:


    hk_b "Thank you for all of your hard work. You don't have to come see me any longer. {w}I never shared your secrets, and I hope..."


translate English day10_hk_3930b7df:


    hk_b "Actually, you can do whatever the hell you want. {w}Because soon enough, it'll be your secret alone."


translate English day10_hk_28c2bcfd:


    sc "Haku..."


translate English day10_hk_6f147afc:


    nar "Before I can finish, she stands up. {w}All I can do is watch as her figure fades into the distance."


translate English day10_hk_b2060424:


    nar "Everything we shared was nothing more than a game of sorts."


translate English day10_hk_300c3ee2:


    nar "We've shared this symbiotic relationship for a while now where instead of giving ourselves to the other person, we'd merely fill in the missing pieces."


translate English day10_hk_2b3a43c2:


    nar "Just hearing the words \"night\" or \"secret\" filled my stomach with butterflies in a way not befitting my age."


translate English day10_hk_c951caa1:


    nar "I was always afraid she would suddenly revert to her mature face and draw the line at our relationship,"


translate English day10_hk_93c186ac:


    nar "leading me to preemptively distance myself while constantly putting myself down."


translate English day10_hk_bd98cbec:


    nar "I don't need love, and I don't need to feel special. {w}We were nothing more than substitutes in each other's lives."


translate English day10_hk_ff0c0237:


    nar "I always knew our relationship could never last. It was me alone who'd been trapped in a dream."


translate English day10_hk_7a439920:


    nar "She has completely vanished into the darkness. The longest night of my life is slowly passing. {w}And soon, it will be dawn."


