    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_78131f64:



    nvl clear
    "\n I return to my room, but I can't sleep at all."


translate English day11_hk_85ff92a0:


    "I manage to sleep fitfully for about five or ten minutes before the dawn breaks. {w}Fatigue relentless stabs at my brain."


translate English day11_hk_ae1f35bd:


    "I remain in bed for a little while longer, not wanting to get up, before eventually dragging myself out. {w}I need to change the bandages on my fresh wound."


translate English day11_hk_67c40f30:


    et "I stuff the old bandages into a bag and get ready for work. {w}I use my foot to shove aside the mountain of trash bags that are currently blocking access to the door to my room before opening it."


translate English day11_hk_7c99bb6f:



    nvl clear
    "\n It's early enough that everyone is still sound asleep, and I head to the empty bathroom so I can wash myself. The sound of the water falling is painfully loud."


translate English day11_hk_426ee364:


    "The cold which I'm usually thankful for as someone who tends to run hot fills me with disgust today."


translate English day11_hk_4fedca47:


    et "First, I have to deal with the reports that came in during the night and make a list of assignments for the priests in the department which I'll hand out. {w}Also, there's a funeral later today..."


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_e2b1e64b:


    "\n Suddenly, it feels like my brain has contracted to the size of a pea, and I'm assaulted by a painful ringing in my ears."


translate English day11_hk_9807fa9b:


    "There's still no one around. I sit down on the ground and catch my breath."


translate English day11_hk_c1f6d66f:


    "My heart is pounding wildly in my chest. I have no idea why... {w}Though this isn't the first time I've had a reaction like this."


translate English day11_hk_61de2b55:


    "As I sit there, crouched over, the wound in my stomach I received just the night before begins throbbing again. {w}Considering I'd been in the infirmary all night, I figured it'd be fine by now..."


translate English day11_hk_f6141f79:


    et "That it still hurts creates a dull rage inside me. I can't help but feel my body is nothing more than a burden."


translate English day11_hk_305e620f:



    nvl clear
    "\n And then I begin my work day. {w}Time passes quickly as I busily run from one place to another, preoccupied with the tasks that need to get done."


translate English day11_hk_83815df2:


    "I feel blessed that time seems to be moving as fast as it is. {w}I can't wait for it to be night again..."


translate English day11_hk_fe1323ac:


    et "I put an end to that thought and am immediately assaulted by a wave of nausea. {w}I find myself on the verge of vomiting several times, but eventually manage to hold it back. Good thing my stomach's empty."


translate English day11_hk_be27e13f:


    nar "It's midday, meaning it's time to report to the bishop about yesterday's documents. I sigh heavily as I count the pages I hold in my hand."


translate English day11_hk_f838a10e:


