    "Once you admit what a good for nothing piece of trash you are, there's no going back to the way things were."


translate English day11_hk_6998fff5:


    et "I didn't have the courage to admit to what I'd done. {w}Because I was trapped in this suffocating situation where I couldn't have my way, I felt like I needed to redirect my rage and hatred away from myself..."


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_3a0cd69e:


    et "\n Each cruel memory carries its own weight. A simple word of apology seems far too light to act as a counterbalance."


translate English day11_hk_1d519b3c:


    nar "Maya slowly follows me, her shoulders trembling faintly."


translate English day11_hk_5bb5d321:


    nar "They feel so thin and scrawny as I guide her forward, my arm wrapped around them."


translate English day11_hk_4021fd13:


    nar "I assume Maya wants me dead because of what happened the other night."


translate English day11_hk_996bd507:


    nar "Which is why I was honestly surprised when I saw Maya cling so desperately to [na] with her frail body."


translate English day11_hk_f287a2ec:


    nar "She hates me with every fiber of her being, that much is true, but I get the feeling there's still some lingering affection for me hidden beneath her resentment."


translate English day11_hk_404dacae:


    nar "When we eventually stop walking, Maya looks up at me. {w}Her nose and her eyes are swollen bright red."


translate English day11_hk_8f48341b:


    sc "Maya..."


translate English day11_hk_966fdc0c:


    nar "I grimace as I struggle to figure out whether I should say \"thanks\" or \"I'm sorry\" first."


translate English day11_hk_53cd3aad:


    nar "Seeing my hesitation, her expression crumbles."


translate English day11_hk_192cac46:


    nar "The tears that had stopped resume pouring down her face, and a pained moan escapes her throat."


translate English day11_hk_cc708157:


    nar "She then balls her hand into a fist and punches me incredibly slowly once, then twice."


translate English day11_hk_08a64646:


    nar "The force behind her attack is so weak that I don't understand what she's doing until the third blow."


translate English day11_hk_d15c01bd:


    my "I hate you..."


translate English day11_hk_67eddc04:


    nar "Once she stops moving, I just as slowly place my hand on her back."


translate English day11_hk_253cf30a:


    nar "She wraps her arms around me almost painfully tight while bawling loudly."


translate English day11_hk_5f7d9e37:


    nar "My clothes are gradually getting soaked through by her flood of tears, but I continue holding her without making a move to push her away."


translate English day11_hk_215467be:


    nar "I gently rub her trembling back."


translate English day11_hk_313babd1:


    nar "We stand there for a moment longer before disengaging the hug."


translate English day11_hk_a1deda30:


    nar "As I turn down a different hall on my way back to the department office, I see [na] running away from where I am."


translate English day11_hk_355c428a:


    nar "I hurry over to the door, stopping in front of it."


translate English day11_hk_e90ea09d:


    nar "I'm happy at first to see he's okay, but then I wonder if that means something happened to Haku."


translate English day11_hk_e72e525a:


    nar "I'm afraid to imagine what lies in wait inside."


translate English day11_hk_c2cd5756:


    nar "Just then, the door opens."


translate English day11_hk_59f7641e:


    sc "Whoa..." with sshake


translate English day11_hk_29d49261:


    hk_b "ACK?!" with sshake


translate English day11_hk_38aad432:


    nar "Haku takes a step back, a look of surprise on her face. I look at her with a similar expression mirrored on mine. {w}I thought my heart stopped for a moment there."


translate English day11_hk_e62a1cd6:


    nar "She glances away to avoid my gaze, I grab her face in my hands and force her to look at me."


translate English day11_hk_7d4c9167:


    sc "That's quite the look you got there..."


translate English day11_hk_cd932636:


    nar "My hand trembles as I touch her beat-up face. I can't seem to stop trembling even after I let go, and it soon spreads throughout my entire body."


translate English day11_hk_511aae3e:


    hk_b "Don't get the wrong idea."


translate English day11_hk_2ad8c131:


    nar "She says while gingerly patting her bruised and swollen cheek."


translate English day11_hk_736b6461:


    hk_b "I didn't lose, I let him do this to me... That brat's got a killer left hook."


translate English day11_hk_d52dd81c:


    sc "..."


translate English day11_hk_e43e6ea4:


    hk_b "So now you're crying."


translate English day11_hk_79da0687:


    nar "Surprised, I hastily wipe at my eyes. {w}There's a bit of moisture, but it could just as easily be sweat."


translate English day11_hk_198785d7:


    sc "...I'm not crying."


translate English day11_hk_3d871dd0:


    hk_b "Ha ha! All I did was guide a lost lamb back onto the right path, as any bishop would do. It was nothing personal."


translate English day11_hk_04fd3077:


    hk_b "So don't feel like this is somehow your fault."


translate English day11_hk_77791284_1:


    sc "..."


translate English day11_hk_9b92aa09:


    hk_b "More importantly, you're one to talk about looks. You're way more beat-up than I am."


translate English day11_hk_cdb7b3bf:


    sc "It doesn't matter what I look like! There's no way you can go out in public with your face all banged up like that! {w}You need to get some medical care, right now..."


translate English day11_hk_2fbac0e4:


    hk_b "In that case..."


translate English day11_hk_71c3797a:


    hk_b "Will you come back to my room?"


translate English day11_hk_bc0f886e:


    nar "For the first time in quite a while, we head back to the dorms together."


translate English day11_hk_daac7102:


    nar "The moment we reach the door to her room on the quiet first floor, Haku pauses for a moment."


translate English day11_hk_ed79e51a:


    hk_b "Securett, key."


translate English day11_hk_1eed3ea8:


    sc "Hm?"


translate English day11_hk_8ceb732a:


    nar "Oh, right, I mumble quietly. {w}I take the spare key to her room out of my pocket, the metal still shining."


translate English day11_hk_f451ca78:


    hk_b "I figured you still had it. {w}Give it back."


translate English day11_hk_7275d42f:


    nar "I place it in her waiting hand."


translate English day11_hk_43dba158:


    nar "I watch silently as she puts the key in the keyhole and then turns her wrist to unlock the door."


translate English day11_hk_ade0a040:


    sc "Why?"


translate English day11_hk_84a8d65b:


    hk_b "Why? Well, because... it's always open anyway."


translate English day11_hk_c6d33869:


    nar "The door opens at the same time I speak those words that only just come to mind. {w}Despite this being a place I stop by practically everyday, I find myself on edge for some reason."


translate English day11_hk_326f1a11:


    nar "The candle placed in an ash tray next to her bed has already melted completely."


translate English day11_hk_8c4eb229:


    hk_b "What are you so fascinated by, Securett? Don't look over there."


translate English day11_hk_73e0e627:


    sc "You haven't been sleeping well lately either?"


translate English day11_hk_a958f8b0:


    hk_b "Not like before. Though the nightmares bother me less now. {w}I find the more I work, the less I sleep."


translate English day11_hk_c7a818f2:


    sc "Yeah?"


translate English day11_hk_528e9f1c:


    nar "I assumed that as soon as we got back, we'd settle into our usual conversation patterns and I'd get to work cleaning her up,"


translate English day11_hk_a1ff9f68:


    nar "but just like me, Haku begins wandering around her room, peeking into cupboards."


translate English day11_hk_a687533d:


    nar "I continue my cursory investigation, which is when I spot the trash bag left next to the bookcase."


translate English day11_hk_eb6e5668:


    nar "Inside the transparent bag are some of Haku's favorite movies."


translate English day11_hk_0bce8764:


    nar "She especially loves action and epic films, but there are others as well."


translate English day11_hk_28ebc90e:


    hk_b "Hey, hey, hey! You're not a mouse, so don't go snooping through my stuff."


translate English day11_hk_5c346901:


    sc "Are you throwing these out? But you used to watch this every day...{w} Potatocide Squad or something like that."


translate English day11_hk_39b99211:


    hk_b "It's all there, even the original series. {w}Heh! I've been watching those movies since I officially became an adult."


translate English day11_hk_4fb05cb7:


    hk_b "But it's finally time to graduate from doing so. It's time to focus on my work."


translate English day11_hk_60b28489:


    nar "Haku, who's been pacing her room since we stepped forward inside, suddenly comes back with a black bottle and two glasses. {w}I know it's alcohol without needing to ask."


translate English day11_hk_b09d28dd:


    sc "Haku..."


translate English day11_hk_9971a2a2:


    nar "She answers with a silent smile. It's the first actual smile she's ever shown me, though I get the feeling it's the type you give when you're faking a response."


translate English day11_hk_a40838c2:


    nar "Not only that, but it's accompanying an offer to drink."


translate English day11_hk_c418c556:


    nar "Despite knowing that I gave up both drinking and smoking around the time I started meeting her in the forest chapel."


translate English day11_hk_9d1dc65b:


    sc "I thought I came here to get you bandaged up? What about work?"


translate English day11_hk_9aadde51:


    hk_b "You don't have to worry about that. Patients shouldn't be working anyway, right?"


translate English day11_hk_10ec936d:


    sc "Should a patient really be drinking though? Besides... {w}I'm still abstaining."


translate English day11_hk_aa3717ca:


    hk_b "If an adult gives the okay, then what's the harm?"


translate English day11_hk_f307f45d:


    sc "Do you always keep this kind of stuff in here?"


translate English day11_hk_3d8650e2:


    hk_b "Of course. I use one of the shelves as a liquor cabinet."


translate English day11_hk_c93f4cd2:


    sc "So you live here in the dorms as some weird hobby or...?"


translate English day11_hk_c0b21cc5:


    hk_b "Well... There's no space for me in my father's house. {w}Now come on, you gotta use both hands."


translate English day11_hk_9d3c677c:


    nar "Just one sip of the clear brown liquid is enough to leave my throat feeling raw."


translate English day11_hk_26075ae2:


    nar "The liquor is cool yet it stings my esophagus going down, causing my stomach to quickly heat up."


translate English day11_hk_5c10413e:


    nar "It has a somewhat bitter aftertaste and a smell like charred wood fills my nose. {w}Oof... Isn't this the kind of liquor you need to dilute with something when you drink it?"


translate English day11_hk_b1240240:


    sc "This is... expensive stuff."


translate English day11_hk_9cd0181e:


    hk_b "I had no doubt you'd love it."


translate English day11_hk_7d211a3a:


    nar "She quickly gulps down the potent liquid despite the fact that the inside of her mouth is probably riddled with open wounds. It's like she's trying to get drunk as fast as possible."


translate English day11_hk_418d9acd:


    hk_b "Securett... Do you remember your real name?"


translate English day11_hk_556da8ca:


    nar "Haku suddenly asks me. I'm used to these kind of random questions from her at this point."


translate English day11_hk_7f84dae6:


    sc "My name? {w}What's the point of remembering that now? Everyone already knows me as Securett."


translate English day11_hk_b0353e7e:


    hk_b "I really think you should treat it with more care than that. After all, a name harbors a person's destiny, their very life!"


translate English day11_hk_b3d0f09f:


    hk_b "Not like what you're saying is wrong, though."


translate English day11_hk_97f83edd:


    hk_b "If other people call you by a certain name, even if it's not your true name, that will eventually also become your name."


translate English day11_hk_791dd065:


    sc "If that's true, then what would you prefer to be called?"


translate English day11_hk_ff6db6e3:


    hk_b "Me? Good question... {w}Hero maybe..."


translate English day11_hk_2b6ccbf5:


    nar "She falls silent following that statement and closes her eyes, as if savoring her drink."


translate English day11_hk_f49cb14f:


    nar "As if finding the right moment to say what she's afraid of."


translate English day11_hk_0f3e96d0:


    nar "Shortly after, she says something that would make anyone in the world horrified if they heard her."


translate English day11_hk_292386ad:


    hk_b "I killed Arne Alternata."


translate English day11_hk_7eb5287a:


    nar "This morning, or last night to be more precise, Arne Alternata was found dead."


translate English day11_hk_bd1f303f:


    nar "Rumors said a suspicious man attacked her, and that her brother who'd been with her at the time brought back her body."


translate English day11_hk_ee96471a:


    nar "Seeing the intensity in her eyes as she made that declaration, as if asserting an obvious truth, I can't help but feel afraid."


translate English day11_hk_49a91f79:


    nar "I can't bring myself to look away, and yet at the same time, I can't even bring myself to nod in response."


translate English day11_hk_daf60ada:


    sc "I see..."


translate English day11_hk_60c62c41:


    nar "I end up giving that idiotic answer. {w}She frowns and shakes her head."


translate English day11_hk_5d3e706d:


    nar "Unlike usual, it appears she wants me to ask why."


translate English day11_hk_f5ad8c50:


    sc "Why did you do it?"


translate English day11_hk_2f09e0a0:


    hk_b "To explain that, we need to go back a long ways first..."


translate English day11_hk_f2e04a01:


    sc "I want to hear everything."


translate English day11_hk_ceae483c:


    nar "Haku nods. The empty part of the softly shimmering glass bottle glitters purple. {w}And with that, she begins her outrageous story."


translate English day11_hk_f9da57f6:


    hk_b "Ever since I was a child, I've been desperate for my father's affection."


translate English day11_hk_a529a7ce:


    hk_b "He's always been a calm and quiet man, so I knew there must be some special reason that he chose me out of every other child to adopt as one of his own."


translate English day11_hk_30d9d460:


    hk_b "I was sure that reason was most likely terrifying, but I was prepared to face whatever it may be."


translate English day11_hk_2d45b763:


    hk_b "Since I began living with him, my father has only called to see me three times."


translate English day11_hk_d1405c76:


    sc "That sounds pretty problematic..."


translate English day11_hk_1a731cd7:


    hk_b "We all have our own unique family situations. The first time, he ordered me to kill a small animal."


translate English day11_hk_15b5ea88:


    hk_b "I'm talking, like, a rabbit or a cat. {w}The only other words he said to me after handing me the knife were \"do it.\""


translate English day11_hk_22d20c96:


    hk_b "So I was forced to kill an animal in front of him."


translate English day11_hk_47cb6949:


    nar "Haku hates animals. {w}I never saw it as that big of a deal since it's not that uncommon for people to hate animals."


translate English day11_hk_0ac842bf:


    nar "Though now that I have this new piece of information, I get the feeling she doesn't necessarily dislike them, but has a strong aversion to them due to an altogether different emotion."


translate English day11_hk_f6ac8579:


    hk_b "Once I became used to killing animals, I found myself standing in front of a human that was tied up in place of where beasts once stood."


translate English day11_hk_0fcbfdce:


    hk_b "My father gave me the knife like always, but as a young kid, I told him there was no way I could do it."


translate English day11_hk_0d2673cd:


    hk_b "And then... he kicked me out of the house. That was far scarier than any punishment I could have imagined."


translate English day11_hk_4f691e2c:


    hk_b "That's how I began killing people."


translate English day11_hk_0c70d149:


    sc "Is that what ultimately led to your mental break?"


translate English day11_hk_273cd078:


    hk_b "Trying to speculate on a definitive cause for a mental illness is nothing more than a waste of time."


translate English day11_hk_521f4d8b:


    hk_b "With that said... I won't deny my view on the world has grown warped ever since then."


translate English day11_hk_a51afe05:


    hk_b "I wasn't that obedient or docile of a child to begin with, but from that point forward, I really went nuts in the direct meaning of the term."


translate English day11_hk_e2abaea4:


    hk_b "I screamed my head off day and night and destroyed everything in sight. My thoughts were consumed by the desire to drive other people mad."


translate English day11_hk_1c5973b7:


    hk_b "Everyone pointed at me and said I was possessed by some evil demon. {w}Which is when I was forced to undergo an exorcism."


translate English day11_hk_52d18b92:


    sc "What's that?"


translate English day11_hk_f7fae2af:


    hk_b "A ritual common in rural towns. {w}They take you to a stable where an old man who claims to be an expert on the matter forces you to perform like a puppet on a string."


translate English day11_hk_7c0705cb:


    hk_b "They made me drink animal blood, threw me naked into a pit of snakes, and also drained me of my own blood. {w}Virginal blood, because..."


translate English day11_hk_ac760e65:


    nar "The moment she says those words, she clamps her mouth shut and when she looks up at me, I get the feeling there must be a reason why."


translate English day11_hk_5295bf0a:


    nar "As soon as I realize, my breathing becomes unsteady with anxiety and concern."


translate English day11_hk_37e0253f:


    nar "My head throbs and my heart hurts to the point where I'm sure I must be right."


translate English day11_hk_33226184:


    hk_b "I feel like you jumped to the wrong conclusion. I'm right, aren't I?"


translate English day11_hk_b3d719f2:


    hk_b "The type of person who deals in rituals like that have gone crazy from their own religion because a sane person would never even consider sleeping with a demon, right?"


translate English day11_hk_53d222fa:


    sc "...What happened then?"


translate English day11_hk_e2171333:


    hk_b "An exorcism is all about using somewhat unorthodox methods on the afflicted person's body and psyche..."


translate English day11_hk_2361b521:


    hk_b "...in order to drag the offending spirit out."


translate English day11_hk_6fdd5b0e:


    hk_b "Which is why inhuman and non verbal beasts are commonly used. {w}What I'm saying is..."


translate English day11_hk_31e2707b:


    nar "She tips her empty glass towards herself and after taking a tip of air, she chuckles softly with her mouth closed."


translate English day11_hk_1a64d176:


    nar "It's the same smile she gave me at the start of her story. One meant only to hide the truth."


translate English day11_hk_94f04190:


    nar "But I already understand the part she left out."


translate English day11_hk_41f4040b:


    nar "I throw the glass I'd been holding down before standing up. My entire body is shaking." with sshake


translate English day11_hk_066fbe9e:


    nar "Haku hates dark, cold places. {w}And she especially detests dogs."


translate English day11_hk_4feda46f:


    nar "She says she has difficulty sleeping and suffers from constant nightmares..."


translate English day11_hk_e7fdd0bf:


    nar "The image of young Haku, a version of her I've never seen, crosses my mind. {w}She's pale, but not in the normal sense."


translate English day11_hk_f371c322:


    nar "My face flushes with heat as I stand there, shaking with rage. {w}My head doesn't hurt, but my mind is in a state of chaotic confusion."


translate English day11_hk_0c3c7751:


    nar "Which each staccato heartbeat, the space between my thighs grow increasingly itchy and hot."


translate English day11_hk_58a5c5e9:


    nar "What I'm feeling isn't rage or shock. It's something close to arousal... {w}In that moment, I want to die."


translate English day11_hk_605ed02c:


    hk_b "The second order my father gave me was to work at the temple."


translate English day11_hk_124b8efd:


    nar "She looks at me silently for a moment before continuing her story as if nothing happened."


translate English day11_hk_d1480abc:


    hk_b "And after three years had passed, the Cleanup Department came into being."


translate English day11_hk_de02903a:


    hk_b "Have you ever once doubted its existence?"


translate English day11_hk_4eb909ba:


    hk_b "Or wonder how such a convenient department might have so suddenly appeared, right when it was most needed?"


translate English day11_hk_6f42ac5f:


    sc "Get to the point."


translate English day11_hk_5e5d985c:


    hk_b "What exactly does the department symbolize to you?"


translate English day11_hk_10475b1a:


    sc "Isn't it a department created to help the living?"


translate English day11_hk_c8518427:


    hk_b "Indeed. {w}It is for the people who will continue living hereafter. And as thus, we specialize in collecting human sacrifices."


translate English day11_hk_0b79476c:


    nar "She slowly gets to her feet before looking down at me."


translate English day11_hk_83278f16:


    nar "We're both clearly intoxicated at this point, with both of us being unsteady on our feet."


translate English day11_hk_652d6696:


    hk_b "Do you know about this Great Calamity that befalls the earth once every 2,000 years or so? {w}That was the third order my father gave me."


translate English day11_hk_e57c541a:


    hk_b "A large hole is dug in the center of the capital where Pestis congregates the most heavily, and a sacrifice is buried within it."


translate English day11_hk_14be8c6b:


    hk_b "The sacrifice is given to God, who art in Heaven above, so that humankind may remain living on the land he has lent us."


translate English day11_hk_200ae483:


    hk_b "All of my childhood training was in preparation for this singular event."


translate English day11_hk_77791284_2:


    sc "..."


translate English day11_hk_40f1303c:


    hk_b "Since priests cannot disobey God's will, all bishops are obligated to perform this ritual."


translate English day11_hk_c94911a5:


    hk_b "Except for those from the Magic Department who were too distracted by their own familial issues to get the message."


translate English day11_hk_d649c0ed:


    hk_b "Which is why we decided to sacrifice the priests from the Magic Department since they hold the most sacred power in the temple along with the priests from the Cleanup Department, down and out kids with nowhere to go."


translate English day11_hk_9eba8a9b:


    sc "But I thought all the priests who voluntarily retire go back home?"


translate English day11_hk_4d324779:


    nar "She smirks while giving me a look that seems to say, oh you dear, sweet child. {w}She's never looked at me that way before."


translate English day11_hk_b7f3815a:


    hk_b "That's clearly not the case then. {w}Because what I'm telling you, Securett, is the truth..."


translate English day11_hk_89688d92:


    hk_b "Two people were sacrificed the other day, one of whom was that young blonde lady."


translate English day11_hk_14efa3fe:


    hk_b "It was kind of a mess due to the circumstances surrounding her departure, which wasn't entirely by choice, but thankfully I had the sin she'd committed as a conveniently adequate cover story."


translate English day11_hk_937177fe:


    sc "Then what about the official priests? What are they doing?"


translate English day11_hk_90a1706a:


    hk_b "They're taught the truth of what goes on in the temple and are given the chance to help collect appropriate sacrifices. Though if they refuse... {w}Let's just say, it's not in their best interests to do so."


translate English day11_hk_1761c850:


    sc "You... You kept listening to me vent this whole time without saying a word despite knowing all that?"


translate English day11_hk_512ce802:


    sc "You knew how worried I was about the new recruits. You knew everything... {w}I don't understand..."


translate English day11_hk_12ab39ff:


    hk_b "I couldn't be up front with you because you're not yet an official priest. That's all there was to it."


translate English day11_hk_f7a8a786:


    nar "Up until yesterday, I would have been shocked or angry upon hearing any of this."


translate English day11_hk_b2dcf0c6:


    nar "Because this is about all the desperate hopelessness I can bear to accept."


translate English day11_hk_707f49a8:


    nar "The truth that has endlessly shrouded my life is dark and guilt-ridden, holding me down with its crushing weight."


translate English day11_hk_fea40b82:


    sc "Everything you've done... You're no hero. You're nothing more than a disgusting murderer..."


translate English day11_hk_c2697b00:


    nar "I don't think anyone has the right to pass judgment on others, but those who commit a crime certainly deserve appropriate punishment."


translate English day11_hk_b3d02c51:


    nar "If her actions truly did prevent some kind of global catastrophe, then her sin would be whitewashed and no one would be held accountable for the monstrosities committed."


translate English day11_hk_d08d5558:


    hk_b "The plan is that once the sacrifices have been gathered together, we'll set them ablaze in that hole."


translate English day11_hk_45c172d9:


    nar "She continues talking with a forlorn look in her eyes that lacks even a hint of good cheer."


translate English day11_hk_d55289e7:


    hk_b "Before that could happen, we needed to hunt down the head of the Magic Department, Erzsebet Alternata, and then kill all the priests in his department along with the remaining priests in the Cleanup Department."


translate English day11_hk_f4fba3e5:


    hk_b "Tomorrow. {w}Tomorrow... I'll finally become a hero."


translate English day11_hk_dbfb69ea:


    hk_b "To those looking in from the outside, I'll be a hero who brought down a corrupt and blood-sucking mage,"


translate English day11_hk_b70719aa:


    hk_b "and to those behind the scenes of this operation, they'll know me as a hero who prevented the catastrophic extermination of the human race."


translate English day11_hk_71fbbb19:


    sc "But doesn't that mean you'd be eradicating the entire Magic Department? {w}Do you really think such an idiotic plan will work?"


translate English day11_hk_68dfdb79:


    hk_b "What part seems impossible to you exactly?"


translate English day11_hk_2b9f310a:


    hk_b "Once Alternata is crushed, the old geezers from the Society of Mages will come crawling to my father."


translate English day11_hk_4d9434a4:


    hk_b "Which will make it all the easier in choosing a new mage to take his place."


translate English day11_hk_ff252f20:


    hk_b "But also... we can worry about the aftermath later. For now, we should really be focusing on the Great Calamity itself."


translate English day11_hk_e13f97ea:


    sc "But I thought you loved them! {w}I know that Auxiliary Bishop Grette would never agree to any of this."


translate English day11_hk_d82f664b:


    sc "And neither would the bishop of the Health Department! {w}Plus all those kids in the Disposal Squad who have been working alongside you this whole time...!"


translate English day11_hk_907b851d:


    sc "You would betray everyone who ever loved you?!" with sshake


translate English day11_hk_51ddb72f:


    hk_b "Thousands of lives hang in the balance based on my actions. {w}And of those thousands, there are a handful of people I've loved."


translate English day11_hk_9ad92ff5:


    hk_b "If I had to choose between the two, I would naturally pick those thousands over the few."


translate English day11_hk_0f4636ce:


    sc "Even after all this time, you would do something like this in hopes of getting your father's attention and love?"


translate English day11_hk_baa7f827:


    hk_b "In the end, I was never able to get close to that man in any sense of the word, but one thing has become certain to me over the past few days."


translate English day11_hk_ff9c3eb5:


    hk_b "And that is this so-called divine being known as my father is nothing more than a mortal man cast from ordinary flesh and with ordinary human blood running through his veins..."


translate English day11_hk_d19a6aae:


    hk_b "We will never be able to complete our goals if we forever remain trapped in the illusion of weak-willed cowardice."


translate English day11_hk_a411efbb:


    nar "A dull anger begins rising in my chest, exasperating the growing ache in my head. {w}I look at Haku who's still right in front of me while pressing my hands against my temples."


translate English day11_hk_4e56a140:


    nar "There is no doubt she is Haku Eckaran."


translate English day11_hk_99dac408:


    nar "Someone I once thought knew me well, who knew me better than I knew myself..."


translate English day11_hk_3866a1c1:


    nar "And though I've known for a while now that wasn't actually true,"


translate English day11_hk_b6479d91:


    nar "I'm not sure why the realization that neither of us actually knows anything about the other fills me with such sadness."


translate English day11_hk_d52dd81c_1:


    sc "..."


translate English day11_hk_eeada374:


    sc "Why are you telling me this?"


translate English day11_hk_03638938:


    nar "The question I end up blurting out is one that, until this point, had remained taboo between us."


translate English day11_hk_4ba3b01e:


    nar "For a moment, she merely blinks in surprise as if she'd known I'd held back this entire time and thus had not been expecting me to ever ask at all."


translate English day11_hk_faf97cae:


    nar "To my intoxicated brain, she appears to be moving in slow motion."


translate English day11_hk_2f4cebe2:


    nar "But then her expression reverts back to the one I've come to know well as she speaks in a dark, somber tone."


translate English day11_hk_9ebc11dc:


    hk_b "Well... because I don't really have anyone else I can talk to about this kind of stuff."


translate English day11_hk_36613f84:


    hk_b "I wasn't lying when I said I enjoyed the time we spent together. {w}You hold a special place in my heart."


translate English day11_hk_d0449a9f:


    hk_b "Which is why I want you to know the truth so you can survive. {w}This is the only way I can show my love for you..."


translate English day11_hk_b80afb1f:


    nar "You fucking bitch. {w}I can feel my heart pounding violently in my chest alongside my growing hatred. My heart has never beat this hard before."


translate English day11_hk_875de473:


    nar "Actually, that's a lie. I've had this same reaction every time I was with her."


translate English day11_hk_d223c64d:


    nar "If she'd never looked at me that way, if I'd never been exposed to her darkness, we would have remained strangers forever."


translate English day11_hk_1052fe77:


    nar "In that moment, I realize I love her."


translate English day11_hk_88e64491:


    hk_b "I know how much you wanted to become the auxiliary bishop, yet things would've been so much easier if you'd stayed my temporary assistant forever."


translate English day11_hk_3ba43a4b:


    hk_b "There are certain freedoms lost alongside the official position, and yet as long as you retained your temporary status, you could have left whenever you wanted."


translate English day11_hk_e7ce9e4a:


    sc "But I... I never wanted that!" with sshake


translate English day11_hk_49f677cb:


    hk_b "I did. I wanted nothing more than for you to be able to leave the Underworld and live your own life."


translate English day11_hk_ed2fe43f:


    hk_b "I think highly of you, so please... don't let me down."


translate English day11_hk_dce26f10:


    nar "She begins walking away with her usual fluid gait. {w}It's a bizarre sight to witness."


translate English day11_hk_f8446f88:


    nar "Despite learning the horrific truth, despite the wholehearted betrayal, despite knowing what a disgusting murderer she is..."


translate English day11_hk_c4cc863e:


    nar "I still can't help but see her as brutally and utterly beautiful."


translate English day11_hk_3bed5e88:


    nar "She finally hands me a bottle. Golden liquor shimmers within its transparent glass walls."


translate English day11_hk_c01cd239:


    hk_b "I'd planned on giving this to you as a gift to celebrate your promotion."


translate English day11_hk_8e15a955:


    hk_b "Though we can never be together, we remain united in our hearts. So what does it matter, right?"


translate English day11_hk_4f7d4d30:


    nar "I don't want to take it from her. {w}Because in doing so, I'd admit that my long held goal was nothing more than an illusion."


translate English day11_hk_fad8ee6b:


    nar "I didn't want to accept the fact that she'd deceived me. {w}And yet, I remain alive."


translate English day11_hk_9e60a3f2:


    nar "And I owe my life to that meaningless goal she granted me."


translate English day11_hk_c98f1c5a:


    nar "I want to speak to her as if nothing's wrong, but I can't stop my voice from shaking. My entire body is shaking."


translate English day11_hk_3fae2b09:


    sc "Haku, I can't condone your actions and I'm unable to support you in your endeavors."


translate English day11_hk_caa30c1f:


    sc "And yet despite everything I now know, I still want to do what I can to make you happy..."


translate English day11_hk_eeb1488e:


    hk_b "Stop that. {w}That kind of thinking will do you in."


translate English day11_hk_7585557b:


    hk_b "Instead of leaving your life in my hands, be honest and admit YOU want to be happy. {w}Live your life with confidence and with dignity."


translate English day11_hk_f505db16:


    hk_b "Just as I am myself, you are really *you*, Securett. {w}I want you to continue living... even after I'm gone."


translate English day11_hk_6f075b8a:


    nar "I don't know how to answer that. {w}With Haku's full attention on me, I find it impossible to look away."


translate English day11_hk_5b99ce15:


    nar "The smooth bottle she holds in her hand glimmers softly in the light."


translate English day11_hk_da09a2a4:


    nar "The woman reflected in that surface, once the light fades, looks incredibly young and weak. {w}I hate it. I hate it so much."


translate English day11_hk_cbd87b33:


    nar "I'm only barely able to keep myself from crying out in heartbreak. {w}I'm breathing so heavily that I feel like I might run out of oxygen at any moment."


translate English day11_hk_ae6587b2:


    nar "My body is filled with such an intense heat that it's like I'm on the verge of exploding into nothing."


translate English day11_hk_d84013fd:


    nar "But there's no way I can run away from her. I come to the realization I have to accept my fate with my own two hands."


translate English day11_hk_b9d1d688:


    nar "I take the gift and Haku grabs my shoulder, her expression unwavering."


translate English day11_hk_f0e61d09:


    nar "She turns me around and walks me over to the door. Her gloved hand, the material hard and stiff, is surprisingly heavy."


translate English day11_hk_e6b879d9:


    hk_b "I'm sorry for keeping you. {w}I'll make sure to get my wounds taken care of, okay? Now... goodbye."


translate English day11_hk_a83d992f:


    nar "She gives me the same light-hearted farewell she always does, as if everything we just talked about was nothing more than an alcohol-induced dream."


translate English day11_hk_d4e3ecf5:


    nar "And so I answer her the same way I always do."


translate English day11_hk_7ed35155:


    sc "See you tomorrow."


translate English day11_hk_4f75655c:


    hk_b "...Mm."


translate English day11_hk_a6f5e56a:


    nar "And the door closes."


translate English day11_hk_c7225b52:


    nar "The shadowy hallway I've been kicked out into is as dark as the night, but through the window, I can see the moon has already been replaced by the rising sun."


translate English day11_hk_6149df6e:


    nar "With each step, the liquid in the bottle in my pocket sloshes quietly."


translate English day11_hk_e336e004:


    nar "The soft splashing mixed with my unsteady footsteps as I struggle to remain upright fade in and out of my ears."


translate English day11_hk_199b4402:


    nar "I never wanted to stand next to her. {w}I always wanted to stay just a few steps behind that back."


translate English day11_hk_1fad896a:


    nar "How happy was my life when that's all it took to leave me feeling satisfied?"


translate English day11_hk_a07c203d:


    nar "I always assumed the price to protect that happiness was myself. {w}Despite being the biggest denier of that fact."


translate English day11_hk_2e829a34:


    nar "I slow to a stop, my legs trembling even after. I sit down and take a slow, deep breath."


translate English day11_hk_9ddda8d8:


    nar "My hot breath, drenched in the scent of alcohol, feels like a dagger piercing through my head to the point where I realize I can't stand back up."


translate English day11_hk_eb591bb6:


    nar "I can stop it... I wonder why that specific memory is coming to mind now? {w}It's far too late for that now."


translate English day11_hk_d1b3795a:


    nar "Those heavy words of truth she spoke of."


translate English day11_hk_727a5632:


    nar "It was an outrageous story, and yet it was clear she meant every word that came from her mouth..."


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_3dd735a0:


    "\n Aah! A short scream spills from my mouth. {w}It's the first time I ever heard my voice sound like that." with sshake


translate English day11_hk_07486866:


    "I hurriedly slap one hand over my mouth and the other against my aching heart. {w}The movement is instinctive, similar to the natural reaction of covering a wound when feeling extreme pain."


translate English day11_hk_fc977b62:


    "The bottle drops from my hand, shattering into pieces on the ground. It feels like my skin is being ripped from my body."


translate English day11_hk_50ee1b86:


    et "I crawl on the wet floor like a dying beast, trying as hard as I can to keep from screaming."


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_a05fd021:


    "\n Why? {w}Why did this have to happen? {w}All I wanted was to be happy...!" with sshake


translate English day11_hk_3538ac73:


    "I believed that as long as Haku was happy, I could be, too. I thought I'd done everything I could to guarantee that."


translate English day11_hk_44508f79:


    et "Where did I go wrong? When did everything begin crumbling apart? {w}Is [na] to blame? {w}But [na] was my friend..."


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_9:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_9e71fecd:


    "\n Is it possible that I screwed up somewhere?"


translate English day11_hk_bb194fe6:


    "I thought Haku was the strongest person I knew, and now I can't believe I ever wanted to help her."


translate English day11_hk_4d48c5e3:


    "I can't believe I'd accept her final act of mercy as something so painful."


translate English day11_hk_60bd1339:


    "If she thinks she's doing the right thing, then it must be so. {w}Because the path she walks is always righteous."


translate English day11_hk_d789fd68:


    et "If the people of this day and age won't accept her, then I don't belong here."


translate English day11_hk_e57ff6f5:



    nvl clear
    "\n A white light suddenly fills my vision from out of the darkness. {w}The glimmering light flows feverishly."


translate English day11_hk_5c6af9ea:


    et "I really, truly did love her. Having stumbled upon my most long-held fear, I sob for what seems like eternity."


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_10:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_11:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_f839ca2b:



    nvl clear
    "\n I stand up again, wiping away my tears mixed with sweat. {w}Then I force my eyes open wide so as to keep myself from crying anymore while staring straight ahead."


translate English day11_hk_5465c87f:


    et "The path before me is still incredibly dark. I doubt happiness lays in wait for me, but all I can do is move forward."


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_12:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_dc43db3e:


    "\n The more I trust Haku, the less believable her story becomes. {w}How could she betray the people she cared about, leaving herself completely alone?"


translate English day11_hk_72c2e85e:


    et "There's no way she truly believes any of what she told me. Meaning she must have been lying to both of us."


translate English day11_hk_0366158e:



    nvl clear
    "\n Because until now, she sees her younger self in me."


translate English day11_hk_2c682d95:


    "Every word of advice she gave me were things she wished had been said to her while growing up..."


translate English day11_hk_55e50e77:


    "And though I don't necessarily agree with it, there's no denying we were both born with the same fate."


translate English day11_hk_95bf2e59:


    et "A mud-caked body born to a low-class family, clinging to an eternal grudge. {w}But I know my grudge is filled with lingering desire."


translate English day11_hk_609487f1:



    nvl clear
    "\n God Above, I was so in love with her. The fear I wanted to deny more than anything is now something I'm forced to admit as the truth."


translate English day11_hk_d921e3a0:


    et "I force my legs, drained of strength, back into motion. {w}As I watch the white light coming in through the window, I realize I will never be able to go back there again."


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_13:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_hk_76b2fe88_14:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_1_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_1_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


