    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_1_1095f80b:


    "\n The winter of the first Christmas Eve I ever spent at the temple was so cold, I felt like my ears were about to fall off."


translate English day12_hk_1_c1a88d5f:


    "As I watched the Baptism being performed, I remember feeling nauseous from the sheer number of people around me."


translate English day12_hk_1_cb70bd29:


    "It was a day of festivity, and as such, the mages had placed a ward over the capital thus allowing outsiders to come and go from the temple as they pleased. {w}And there were too many of them."


translate English day12_hk_1_fad586e3:


    et "I was sweating despite the cold, and my legs were shaking. {w}It was at that moment, she took my hand before running off, dragging me behind her."


translate English day12_hk_1_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_1_9258e61d:


    "\n We ran as far as we could go, to a quiet place with no one around but us."


translate English day12_hk_1_1877e77e:


    et "I can't believe we ran through that crowd of people, hand-in-hand! Haku cried out while laughing with delight. What a delightful Christmas Eve! she said."


translate English day12_hk_1_3bce363a:


    sc "Is it not usually as fun as this?"


translate English day12_hk_1_7c0383c1:


    hk_b "Oh, my father hates Christmas Eve. He always has."


translate English day12_hk_1_5f2a2538:


    hk_b "Which is why I don't necessarily like it, but also don't hate it either. I'm ambivalent about the whole thing."


translate English day12_hk_1_f614225c:


    hk_b "But that's all a thing of the past now."


translate English day12_hk_1_ea58ec2d:


    nar "I remember seeing the city spread out before me from that shabby hole-in-the-wall she'd taken us to."


translate English day12_hk_1_397fe1e5:


    nar "There was a creepy black fog that covered the dark sky, making it seem more distant than it was."


translate English day12_hk_1_c3006d5b:


    nar "I saw that and remarked on how scary it was, and yet all Haku could see were the shimmering lights underneath, saying how pretty they were."


translate English day12_hk_1_60047bf5:


    hk_b "What are you looking at, Securett?"


translate English day12_hk_1_5fd1ddc4:


    sc "That... ward placed over the capital."


translate English day12_hk_1_3a2134bb:


    hk_b "So we're looking at the same thing then. The people living in the city. {w}Right?"


translate English day12_hk_1_3c8ee3d8:


    sc "But... I don't understand your view point."


translate English day12_hk_1_b3c59302:


    hk_b "There is value in doing the best you can."


translate English day12_hk_1_7165fedc:


    hk_b "And even when it's impossible for us to think the same way, we can still understand each other's view points."


translate English day12_hk_1_3118c2ab:


    hk_b "You can make today worthwhile by doing so."


translate English day12_hk_1_e438fdb0:


    nar "I thought it was unfair that we could be standing in the same place, buffeted by the same cold wind and yet spend our entire lives looking at the same world in entirely different ways."


translate English day12_hk_1_483d1c76:


    nar "I'm sure that Haku is far more aware of the terrible brutalities of the world around us."


translate English day12_hk_1_3a6672ae:


    hk_b "I was thinking the other day..."


translate English day12_hk_1_adca824f:


    hk_b "That it might be nice to have an assistant of sorts to help me out."


translate English day12_hk_1_12d1b3f2:


    nar "And yet if Haku still believed there was enough to keep living for despite everything that had happened to her, then I wanted her blessing."


translate English day12_hk_1_7bca917a:



    nvl clear
    "\n It's morning. {w}The space under my blankets is cold from tossing and turning all night."


translate English day12_hk_1_985a8a74:


    "My mind turns back to yesterday's events as I watch the pure-white sky spread out before me. {w}Though it'd be more accurate to say I'm thinking of her, as always."


translate English day12_hk_1_e03416c3:


    et "I think of her every morning when I wake up. It's part of my daily routine."


translate English day12_hk_1_f7b039ef:



    nvl clear
    "\n Though the first image that springs to mind is from yesterday, when the Haku I know who always pursued righteousness and justice collided with a disgusting murderer."


translate English day12_hk_1_d22ff1f4:


    "I'm not the only one in a state of agitation. {w}With the major pillar of the Magic Department gone, the normalcy that once existed with the great mage at its center is already falling apart."


translate English day12_hk_1_3fed1445:


    "Once the temple falls, it's only a matter of time until the rest of the world, which relies on the temple for its own sense of normalcy, is shaken as well. {w}Summer has not yet begun, and already the air shimmers with a blaze of heat."


translate English day12_hk_1_72d4a1fe:


    et "I watch the sun as it rises seemingly forever into the sky before frowning."


translate English day12_hk_1_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_1_4fab41c4:


    "\n But time stops for no one, and I have to get to work. {w}Haku gave me the chance to survive, and as long as I'm not dead, there are things I need to do."


translate English day12_hk_1_7c6863c8:


    "Which is how I find myself standing in front of my locker, knowing I need to get the shovel and sack I shoved in there the other day and simply being unable to do so. {w}My hands are frozen, trembling in the air."


translate English day12_hk_1_7cafdff0:


    "The bishop has not yet arrived. {w}I can hear the other priests noisily talking to each other as they wait for her to appear."


translate English day12_hk_1_bce25adc:


    et "As I glance around the suffocating room, everyone suddenly appears small, as if they're a so far, far distance away."


translate English day12_hk_1_5731d360:



    nvl clear
    "\n They're all going to die today. {w}The weight of the truth I was made aware of comes crashing down on me all over again."


translate English day12_hk_1_579a9535:


    "All it would take is for me to open my mouth, and she would be suitably punished."


translate English day12_hk_1_3a6d668f:


    et "But Haku gave me a chance to escape. {w}I remember how the air felt in that spacious village, so different from this cramped office, and the city full of lights."


translate English day12_hk_1_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_1_df4db767:


    "\n I have money. I could have a life full of soft clothes to wear, good food to eat, and large, warm beds to sleep in."


translate English day12_hk_1_f3c4a453:


    et "Imagine that version of myself, perhaps going to the academy and getting the chance to study..."


translate English day12_hk_1_d11763bf:


    pl "Hey."


translate English day12_hk_1_9792a13c:


    nar "I hear a voice speak to me, bringing me back to this chaotic reality. {w}It's [na]."


translate English day12_hk_1_586dd5f5:


    nar "I know who it is almost immediately, though I have no idea what he might want."


translate English day12_hk_1_153b5368:


    sc "Hm? What's the matter?"


translate English day12_hk_1_106ff429:


    nar "My suspicion causes my voice to sound flat and disinterested."


translate English day12_hk_1_d20094df:


    pl "I need to talk to you."


translate English day12_hk_1_eb0e48fb:


    nar "The mystery only deepens with his next words. {w}Talk about what?"


translate English day12_hk_1_f4040600:


    sc "We said everything there needed to be said yesterday."


translate English day12_hk_1_6a9c7f24:


    nar "He looks depressed. He tells me it's something important. {w}I follow him outside."


translate English day12_hk_1_f92c5399:


    nar "Not that I have any reason to trust him ever again, but I also feel like I can't say no either."


translate English day12_hk_1_bd9cc56e:


    sc "What is this about?"


translate English day12_hk_1_d57164c3:


    nar "I honestly couldn't care less, but I decide to ask anyway. His gaze on me is heavy."


translate English day12_hk_1_ea7882a1:


    nar "When I speak up first, he immediately turns away, as if deep in thought."


translate English day12_hk_1_de87fc99:


    pl "...I want to apologize."


translate English day12_hk_1_0097ac0a:


    sc "Apologize?"


translate English day12_hk_1_c729c770:


    pl "I've treated you horribly."


translate English day12_hk_1_120265d3:


    pl "I should have trusted you, but I was so focused on myself that I did terrible..."


translate English day12_hk_1_cb8fda9c:


    pl "...truly despicable things to you. To the point where I probably don't have the right to say this. {w}I'm truly sorry... I mean it."


translate English day12_hk_1_32328978:


    nar "He stops talking as his entire body begins shaking. Which only makes the whole thing worse."


translate English day12_hk_1_9ada4201:


    nar "I simply look at him without speaking as I try to figure out what my next move should be. {w}What the hell am I supposed to say to that?"


translate English day12_hk_1_7e0124d3:


    nar "And then, he grabs my wrist." with sshake


translate English day12_hk_1_de174753:


    nar "It's so sudden. His palm is dripping so much sweat"


translate English day12_hk_1_bcf4b71e:


    nar "that I accidentally let out a startled shriek like a scared young girl."


translate English day12_hk_1_e5379c97:


    pl "I didn't want to ignore you! {w}I was just frustrated that you lied to me!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_1_77f366c9:


    pl "But now I understand that I was simply taking my frustration out on you unfairly, and I feel terrible!"


translate English day12_hk_1_740bdde1:


    pl "I don't expect my words to change anything. {w}We don't have to go back to being friends,"


translate English day12_hk_1_742e236a:


    pl "and you never have to help me ever again. We don't have to exchange pleasantries,"


translate English day12_hk_1_9101cbf2:


    pl "and if you don't even want to see me, that's fine!!!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_1_8bc4fef8:


    pl "But I... I just feel so bad about the horrible things I did to you. {w}I mean it. Really."


translate English day12_hk_1_a951c1ac:


    pl "There's no excuse for what I did, and I'm aware of that. But... {w}Will you at least accept my apology?"


translate English day12_hk_1_a67e8636:


    nar "I can feel his hands trembling. {w}His gaze remains shaky, though he doesn't look away."


translate English day12_hk_1_5fc04270:


    nar "The sound of his heavy breathing echoes loudly. {w}We're alone in this wide-open space... Until now, someone's always been nearby to step in, but in this moment, it's just the two of us."


translate English day12_hk_1_93f9a145:


    nar "The heavy silence feels almost threatening as it weighs us down, crushing us. {w}And then after a long pause, I open my mouth."


translate English day12_hk_1_76d5c8f2:


    sc "Why are you saying this to me?"


translate English day12_hk_1_57e45a46:


    nar "I feel guilty about lying to him."


translate English day12_hk_1_88768f1c:


    nar "I admit that I definitely had a hand in driving him to this point and pushing him over the edge of sanity."


translate English day12_hk_1_fc1b6323:


    nar "Which is why whenever he'd vent his pent-up frustration and anger on me or hit me, I took it because I felt I deserved it."


translate English day12_hk_1_e1973b48:


    nar "And yet throughout it all, he's wanted something from me, and up until the very end, I never understood what that was."


translate English day12_hk_1_95062372:


    nar "Maybe he just wanted us to become friends again?"


translate English day12_hk_1_65a98a78:


    nar "But he destroyed any chance of that happening when he expressed his hatred towards me in that one simple word."


translate English day12_hk_1_df3e69d3:


    nar "So there's no way he could possibly feel that way about me now, right?"


translate English day12_hk_1_91b7c9ea:


    sc "What's been done is done. I wash my hands of the whole mess."


translate English day12_hk_1_4f18a263:


    sc "The only reason I'm mad at you right now is because you took your anger out on someone who should have never been involved."


translate English day12_hk_1_2767d386:


    sc "I told you not to touch Haku, didn't I? {w}She's an incredibly special person to me!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_1_d7b768fe:


    sc "Why did you have to drag her into all of this?"


translate English day12_hk_1_ab0d2a42:


    sc "Why did you have to hurt her? Did you honestly think doing so would somehow make me reconsider our relationship? To reconcile our friendship?"


translate English day12_hk_1_92e4f105:


    sc "No, that's not it, right?"


translate English day12_hk_1_dd958d81:


    sc "What exactly does this have to do with anything? {w}It's over between us. I'm not interested in hearing anything you have to say."


translate English day12_hk_1_0bbd970b:


    sc "If you really want to make things right between us, you'd apologize to Haku!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_1_feb7f7d1:


    nar "I shout at him before taking a choked breath in."


translate English day12_hk_1_10d02982:


    nar "That was the first time I referred to Haku by her name instead of her title in front of someone other than Haku herself. {w}On top of that, I described her as being incredibly special to me."


translate English day12_hk_1_6f398741:


    nar "When I look back at [na], he looks sad and deflated. {w}But any hint of anger that may have existed is long gone."


translate English day12_hk_1_b2da010a:


    nar "I'd always hoped he could have an easier life than the one he currently has."


translate English day12_hk_1_e115121b:


    nar "That he wouldn't have to experience the same mistakes and hardships I'd endured."


translate English day12_hk_1_9e1418e7:


    nar "I realize I can no longer stand by as a silent observer."


translate English day12_hk_1_9ed72783:


    sc "A serious calamity is about to befall the temple. You should find Maya and get the hell out. {w}She's done nothing wrong to deserve this."


translate English day12_hk_1_03f4a4d7:


    nar "Which is why I decide to leave him with the best advice I can give under the circumstances before parting ways. {w}Running as fast I can."


translate English day12_hk_1_bf2116c7:


    nar "His grip on my hand was hard enough that it continues throbbing long after I pulled free."


translate English day12_hk_1_7745fe78:


    nar "That lingering pain has a far more lasting impression than any other memory I have of him."


translate English day12_hk_1_a801da86:



    nvl clear
    "\n I've learned of the crimes Haku's committed, and I've come to find out she's not anywhere near the perfect woman I once saw her as."


translate English day12_hk_1_6d04a858:


    "I now know the dream I've been chasing all this time is nothing more than an illusion."


translate English day12_hk_1_3321413a:


    "I've known for a while, honestly, that my image of her and the person she really was were two completely different things. Perhaps even my feelings for her are a lie as well."


translate English day12_hk_1_86397d36:


    et "But it seems inevitable that something like that might happen, considering how long I've loved her."


translate English day12_hk_1_99ac3a8e:



    nvl clear
    "\n What if I'm not the one Haku has been searching for?"


translate English day12_hk_1_fc8268e6:


    "What if I regret this decision? What if we end up falling short of each other's expectations? What if everything about her, including my once fond memories, become nothing but pain?"


translate English day12_hk_1_968c75cd:


    et "I continue to struggle with those possibilities, even now."


translate English day12_hk_1_4c986a0e:



    nvl clear
    "\n No! Stop thinking that way! {w}I yell at myself for being so weak. Because if I don't, I'll either come to a standstill or stumble and fall." with sshake


translate English day12_hk_1_47a617d2:


    "How in the world did someone like me end up falling for someone like her?"


translate English day12_hk_1_4c353225:


    et "She is... Haku is...!"


translate English day12_hk_1_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_1_82980998:


    "\n The way you twirl your pen between your fingers before writing a sentence. {w}How you always make sure to close your eyes before beginning a long story. {w}Those quirks may seem trivial, but they're special to me."


translate English day12_hk_1_24e60161:


    "Even my name seems to take on an entirely different meaning when I hear it coming from your lips."


translate English day12_hk_1_6069d8b6:


    et "Those who lose themselves in idiosyncrasy are the stupidest of the lower class."


translate English day12_hk_end_9b5fd86e:



    nvl clear
    "{color=#000000}{size=0}{k=0}\n Now let us live in true bliss together. We alone shall forgive and forget whilst surrounded by those who cling to their grudges.{/k}{/size}{fast}{/color}{nw}"


translate English day12_hk_end_97d0f9e9:


    "{color=#000000}{size=0}{k=0}\n Let us live among those who fester with resentment. Free of malice.{/k}{/size}{fast}{/color}{nw}"


translate English day12_hk_end_4f48fb3d:


    nar "I arrive at the usual spot. The smell of moldering corpses rises from the garbage pit."


translate English day12_hk_end_0a05811d:


    nar "I'm sweating despite how cold it is, and my legs are shaking."


translate English day12_hk_end_bea70b61:


    nar "The temple lies in the exact center of the capital where Pestis gathers. {w}A part of me wonders if all those who die pass through this hole in order to return to the place where they were born?"


translate English day12_hk_end_48795ce7:


    nar "When people speak to God, they use only words of worship and praise, yet when they speak of God, he is described as a being that brings down all manner of misfortune on humankind."


translate English day12_hk_end_466b98ec:


    nar "If a life full of such disparate unfairness still has worth, then humans should do what they can to seek that out."


translate English day12_hk_end_8271ce00:


    nar "To, metaphorically speaking, let the light shine in."


translate English day12_hk_end_cae8f43f:


    nar "She's standing there. {w}Bathed in the glow of the relentlessly burning sun that never sets, her eyes glitter golden in the light."


translate English day12_hk_end_71cea607:


    nar "The whiteish stained glass sparkles and dust motes drift lazily through the tall shadows cast by the high ceiling."


translate English day12_hk_end_90e1af77:


    nar "I open my eyes wide as I turn to face the light directly."


translate English day12_hk_end_e73b8023:


    hk_b "I didn't think you'd come... {w}Though I wish you'd trusted me completely."


translate English day12_hk_end_f983a220:


    nar "She doesn't make an attempt to hide her discontent, frowning deeply. With each step, the tip of her sword drags against the ground."


translate English day12_hk_end_310cb6b2:


    nar "The stench of the dead waft from her body."


translate English day12_hk_end_591d20db:


    nar "My heart is pounding so frantically that I feel like it might burst. She's really going to do it."


translate English day12_hk_end_fcf88f8d:


    nar "She came here, not to see me, but offer her sacrifices to the pit. {w}She waves her hand, sending blood flying."


translate English day12_hk_end_13a278da:


    hk_b "It's finally hit me. {w}What about you, Securett? This is the Pestis that man made in order to survive the natural-born one."


translate English day12_hk_end_eccceb0f:


    hk_b "From here on out, everyone will return to the land whence they came, to the bosom of the mother of the current generation of humans--Pestis."


translate English day12_hk_end_dcd309dd:


    hk_b "But in order for this dream to be realized, there must be a judge who can weigh each person's soul."


translate English day12_hk_end_b0031b8f:


    hk_b "So? Do you find me frightening?"


translate English day12_hk_end_cf513fa1:


    nar "She asks in a cold, cruel voice. {w}I've obediently nodded along with whatever she's asked, like she wants me to."


translate English day12_hk_end_7f490883:


    nar "All she wants to hear are her own words parroted back. {w}She has no desire to hear my own."


translate English day12_hk_end_badbbdb4:


    sc "...I find you beautiful."


translate English day12_hk_end_d8fcd5b2:


    sc "I've never seen your eyes look quite like that ever before. {w}I always knew you'd take beautifully to the light, Haku."


translate English day12_hk_end_273a7eda:


    nar "She opens her golden eyes wide in surprise before averting her gaze, purposefully looking away from me."


translate English day12_hk_end_1d864ccb:


    nar "I follow her lead, glancing around."


translate English day12_hk_end_0fbaf3aa:


    nar "The magic once held in this space vanished the moment our relationship was severed."


translate English day12_hk_end_249033d4:


    nar "The pillars that had once appeared so sublimely beautiful with age have turned to nothing but old stones,"


translate English day12_hk_end_188e4974:


    nar "the solemn silence is now gloomy and depressing, and the place is once again filled with a putrid stench as if this is my first time here."


translate English day12_hk_end_912c3294:


    nar "I can't believe such an obvious realization could make me so sad."


translate English day12_hk_end_f5d339be:


    nar "That this space had become something akin to a sanctuary for me before I knew what was happening."


translate English day12_hk_end_4d654445:


    hk_b "I gave you a choice. And yet you chose to come here? For what reason? {w}To die an idiotic death?"


translate English day12_hk_end_dc2a2473:


    sc "No. Becuase I chose you. {w}Because I know you're doing something that deep down, you don't want to."


translate English day12_hk_end_aeeab716:


    sc "Which is why I wanted to talk to you, one last time."


translate English day12_hk_end_84b3eb79:


    hk_b "Sigh... What in the world makes you think that? {w}Just as you are not me, I am likewise not you."


translate English day12_hk_end_5d0d84c9:


    hk_b "Do you truly believe you can convince me?"


translate English day12_hk_end_652aeb21:


    sc "Of course I'm aware we are two completely different people. {w}But our happiness remains connected."


translate English day12_hk_end_1febe404:


    nar "Even if we think differently, we'll always have the memories of our time spent together."


translate English day12_hk_end_b287219e:


    nar "Not necessarily to reminisce or yearn for, but to cherish what once was."


translate English day12_hk_end_40d49d0a:


    sc "I once thought that I was only born in order to serve others."


translate English day12_hk_end_de7b698b:


    sc "I believed it was impossible for me to live solely for myself."


translate English day12_hk_end_87bc4a46:


    sc "But now I understand. {w}I was born to exist for this exact moment."


translate English day12_hk_end_38a05e44:


    sc "You should be given a choice in the same way you gave me one."


translate English day12_hk_end_916ebe00:


    sc "If you truly believe that a person's destiny, that their life is part of one's name,"


translate English day12_hk_end_cf927cea:


    sc "then the person who blessed me with life is none other than you."


translate English day12_hk_end_dc89041e:


    hk_b "..."


translate English day12_hk_end_d61a730b:


    sc "Put down the sword, Haku. {w}I know this is not what you want."


translate English day12_hk_end_84cb0d5e:


    sc "The you I've come to know is a just person who thinks for themselves. They would never kill a bunch of people because someone told them to."


translate English day12_hk_end_dc89041e_1:


    hk_b "..."


translate English day12_hk_end_4122e32c:


    sc "I always wondered why we always met here at the same time every day, and at first, I assumed it had something to do with me."


translate English day12_hk_end_f142870c:


    nar "I take a step closer to her, and she takes one as well. {w}We pass thorugh the spot in the room where the sun is brightest before continuing back into the darkness."


translate English day12_hk_end_208296c2:


    nar "It's as if I'm her shadow."


translate English day12_hk_end_ac3133eb:


    sc "But this was always all about you, wasn't it? Because you wanted a place you could return to, like home."


translate English day12_hk_end_0b0ff081:


    sc "And yet, at the same time, you really didn't want anything to do with your home."


translate English day12_hk_end_ee174d22:


    sc "Why do we always have to \"go back\" or \"return\" somewhere? {w}Let's keep moving forward!"


translate English day12_hk_end_b07c19e8:


    sc "There's a wide world to explore, and we can live our lives while doing so."


translate English day12_hk_end_e555eead:


    sc "Let's forge a new path together!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_end_476ff075:


    hk_b "Securett..."


translate English day12_hk_end_2ab315ab:



    nvl clear
    "{nw}" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_end_75dba7f3:


    nar "As Haku looks at me, her head cocked slightly to the side, she appears to be taking a deep breathe in."


translate English day12_hk_end_948325eb:


    nar "Due in the part to the sun's constant presence in the sky, time seems to stop, or at the very least pass slowly enough as to be almost imperceptible."


translate English day12_hk_end_ab64278c:


    nar "Then she readjusts her grip on the sword. And with an air-splitting swoosh, my vision flashes red then black."


translate English day12_hk_end_8e39780e:


    nar "Cold sweat drips down my neck and back as I struggle to remain upright. {w}With each stagger, I hear what sounds like drops of water hitting the ground."


translate English day12_hk_end_5c65fb57:


    sc "Mngh..." with sshake


translate English day12_hk_end_b5a7b4f4:


    nar "Something hot and foul rushes up my throat and into my nose, and I start coughing in order to get it out." with sshake


translate English day12_hk_end_86960821:


    nar "I taste blood in my trembling throat. A part of me wants nothing more than to scream."


translate English day12_hk_end_d74d575d:


    nar "I raise my head as I try to make sense of the situation, but my vision is far too blurry and dark."


translate English day12_hk_end_0148af02:


    nar "The entire world is fuzzy and dim. {w}I see a white and golden-esque ball of light spill out from within the darkness."


translate English day12_hk_end_69c1c954:


    sc "The... moon...?"


translate English day12_hk_end_944a698b:


    hk_b "You'll never see the moon rise again."


translate English day12_hk_end_0e4d2001:


    nar "I hear Haku's voice and blink my eyes. {w}As her serene face comes into view, my hands begin shaking."


translate English day12_hk_end_2698b146:


    nar "Even though it's not cold at all."


translate English day12_hk_end_80be456c:


    hk_b "The sacrifice is necessary in order to keep the Great Calamity from destroying the Earth."


translate English day12_hk_end_b4b6ac19:


    nar "She's now incredibly close, still holding the sword."


translate English day12_hk_end_ed234a1d:


    nar "Seeing that steadfast determination, I know her life is still perfect, that she still glows with a brilliant light."


translate English day12_hk_end_5051423c:


    nar "I remember the words she spoke to me that day when I was in the same pain I feel now."


translate English day12_hk_end_d6240b27:


    nar "My God, what a devil I was."


translate English day12_hk_end_095bcb08:


    nar "I left scars on what should have been your otherwise perfect life, and misled you into choosing the wrong path."


translate English day12_hk_end_920c23c1:


    nar "Which is what led us to this point, to this spot. {w}So you can make me disappear and in turn, become the perfect hero you've always wanted to be."


translate English day12_hk_end_11cbd3d2:


    hk_b "If only you believed me when I told you this is truly how I feel...!"


translate English day12_hk_end_81269934:


    nar "She points the sword at me without hesitating. Its blade is incredibly sharp, not dull like the knife she held on me last night."


translate English day12_hk_end_bb86219c:


    nar "I can no longer scream thanks to the wound on my neck, which is her way of showing consideration."


translate English day12_hk_end_2c224015:


    nar "Of course it would come to this. {w}I knew it all along."


translate English day12_hk_end_c730ecdb:


    nar "I knew that my desire to help her was nothing more than selfishness on my part."


translate English day12_hk_end_f66efe0a:


    nar "And yet a part of me hoped, perhaps naively, that maybe it might work out."


translate English day12_hk_end_9b37ae69:


    nar "My memory of the deserted office suddenly comes to mind."


translate English day12_hk_end_b90b816f:


    nar "I can still feel the cold sea breeze that always smelled so strongly of fish on my skin from when I worked in the port-side village before coming to the temple."


translate English day12_hk_end_aca3529a:


    nar "Back when I was still scared of so much, I'd dream of going back there."


translate English day12_hk_end_ecd66fda:


    nar "You were right in that, as long as I live, I can always find new friends, find better ways to make a living,"


translate English day12_hk_end_987fd4d6:


    nar "and search for things that bring me happiness while doing so."


translate English day12_hk_end_c7820f49:


    nar "But then who would brush out your hair?"


translate English day12_hk_end_c0fa4712:


    nar "Who would you eat meals with? Who would come to wake you up every morning?"


translate English day12_hk_end_9dbc680f:


    nar "I could easily go on to make different connections, but your nights would forever be colder and sadder."


translate English day12_hk_end_edb412a7:


    nar "And I can't help but worry."


translate English day12_hk_end_9ab223af:


    nar "Which is why I absolutely don't regret coming here."


translate English day12_hk_end_40f14345:


    nar "The strength drains from my body and my legs give way, but I don't fall to the ground. {w}Because she caught me before I could."


translate English day12_hk_end_0b17d56b:


    nar "Even in the hazy darkness, I know it's her arms that are wrapped around my body."


translate English day12_hk_end_dd871ded:


    nar "I feel a faint warmth radiating from her steady hands on the other side of those stiff gloves."


translate English day12_hk_end_a70dffe8:


    nar "I can just make out her outline through my blurred retinas."


translate English day12_hk_end_0399135c:


    nar "I wish I could see her face more clearly so that my memory of her in this moment would be more vibrant."


translate English day12_hk_end_07fa5b39:


    nar "I move my lips in order to speak her name."


translate English day12_hk_end_73dd85c0:


    nar "Nothing comes out, and yet perhaps my intention comes through anyway. I hope so."


translate English day12_hk_end_05bf0615:


    nar "And then, at the very end, her cold blade pierces my heart."


translate English day12_hk_end_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_end_cfa8072e:


    "\n And thus, Securett Rafe dies without making a sound. {w}And as she does, Haku Eckaran drops her sword and cradles her body in both arms."


translate English day12_hk_end_809afd8e:


    "As Haku ruffles Securett's hair, all she can hear from the rapidly cooling body is her own heartbeat."


translate English day12_hk_end_97512dab:


    "Haku looks down at the pool of blood at her feet. {w}The woman reflected back appears pale and incredibly cruel, and yet she is the hero who will save the world from destruction."


translate English day12_hk_end_e83660fe:


    et "Haku takes several deep breaths before picking her sword back up. {w}And then she walks outside."


translate English day12_hk_end_813662f3:



    nvl clear
    "\n Light spills in through the wide-open door, along with a group of ravens who'd been patiently waiting outside."


translate English day12_hk_end_5ed2a4d0:


    "Their messy feathers, splayed in all directions, glimmer pure-white, perhaps due in part to the sun's brilliance."


translate English day12_hk_end_489f9158:


    et "Once in the shadowy darkness, the pure-black birds begin pecking at the dead body. {w}Haku Eckaran watches for a moment before turning away resolutely."


translate English day12_hk_end_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_end_8e36e273:


    "\n Then she steps out into the light. {w}She rips open the hole that exists in the center of the temple riddled with Pestis and drags the blood-soaked bodies out."


translate English day12_hk_end_0f9954cb:


    "All that doth exist in the world shall be hers now. Honor and glory, a blessed life, and her father's approval."


translate English day12_hk_end_dd829f85:


    et "The sun shines brilliantly down on the birth of a queen as she takes her first steps."


translate English day12_hk_end_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_end2_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_end2_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_end2_d52dd81c:


    sc "..."


translate English day12_hk_end2_7917a9a0:


    sc "Sigh..."


translate English day12_hk_end2_89b663c4:


    sc "I knew you'd be here."


translate English day12_hk_end2_020caf14:


    hk_b "Ooh! I didn't think you'd recognize me. {w}I pegged you as some sniveling brat, but I guess you're smarter than you look."


translate English day12_hk_end2_98a1fa9d:


    sc "Says the person who's been following me for the past few days!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_end2_115cb0c2:


    hk_b "I kind of had no choice. I had to make sure you didn't try anything after accidentally noticing me tailing you."


translate English day12_hk_end2_d44ef3c2:


    hk_b "So? {w}What do you plan on doing now? From what I've observed..."


translate English day12_hk_end2_45653c5b:


    hk_b "You're not rash enough to meddle in a stranger's affairs unprovoked, but you also don't strike me as the type to preach about lawful morality."


translate English day12_hk_end2_b55b2877:


    hk_b "It would be amusing to simply watch from afar as your misadventures unfold, but if you're interested, I can let you in on a rather horrifying truth."


translate English day12_hk_end2_b5c9980d:


    hk_b "Ha ha ha!"


translate English day12_hk_end2_b1102d6d:


    sc "I know who you are, even if you don't tell me yourself."


translate English day12_hk_end2_2aa4b377:


    hk_b "Don't feel like you need to make up your mind just yet. Pride goes before the fall, as they say..."


translate English day12_hk_end2_3b37fcd9:


    sc "Begone, evil spirit!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_end2_4e016872:


    hk_b "Whah?"


translate English day12_hk_end2_96484236:


    sc "I have no idea... {w}No idea what you plan on doing with Bishop Haku's body, but I won't let you get away with it!"


translate English day12_hk_end2_b01aaa95:


    hk_b "Whoa, whoa, whoa!!! At least let me finish..."


translate English day12_hk_end2_140b6fc9:


    sc "Shut up!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_end2_6f8493c3:


    hk_b "ACK! {w}You can't just throw salt at me and expect something to happen! Patooie! Patooie!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_end2_625d532b:


    hk_b "I told you I'd tell you the truth!"


translate English day12_hk_end2_0febdd9f:


    sc "And what truth would that be exactly? {w}L-Like I said, I've only been a priest here in the temple for a week or so!"


translate English day12_hk_end2_da1e4b31:


    sc "So don't try anything funny! {w}And d-don't come any closer!"


translate English day12_hk_end2_ac519705:


    hk_b "I'm sad to hear you say that. {w}Of course I know who you are, Securett Rafe. Am I not your bishop?"


translate English day12_hk_end2_9a5b9265:


    hk_b "I have a feeling the two of us are going to get along very well. {w}I was hoping I could persuade you to join me here every night as my conversation companion, but..."


translate English day12_hk_end2_c563fd1e:


    hk_b "Just so you know, I'm what they call a Chatty Cathy. I'll talk your ear off."


translate English day12_hk_end2_81a22085:


    sc "Wh-What kind of nonsense are you...? This place is completely off-limits! Did you really think I'd simply say yes?!"


translate English day12_hk_end2_0fd68bc2:


    sc "Hey! Where are you going?!"


translate English day12_hk_end2_660ab4d4:


    hk_b "You're coming, too. Follow me if you like."


translate English day12_hk_end2_41993122:


    sc "Wh-Where are you taking me?"


translate English day12_hk_end2_596499d0:


    hk_b "You... like drinking, right?"


