    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_2_ce8b2e98:


    "\n Good evening. I'm sorry it's so late. {w}It's just... I just couldn't take it any longer."


translate English day12_hk_2_f0a5fdfd:


    et "I want you to know that she's a sinner--and the sin she's burdened with is far too heavy for her to bear by herself."


translate English day12_hk_2_5df7cbc1:



    nvl clear
    "\n I met her last fall. {w}And although the time I've spent with her pales in comparison to the rest of you,"


translate English day12_hk_2_286c9c27:


    extend " I'm the only one who is aware of the sins she has committed, making the length of our relationship until now irrelevant."


translate English day12_hk_2_79c37807:


    et "To most people, she is nothing but a righteous and beautiful person, however, I know the truth. {w}She's a bold and self-driven woman."


translate English day12_hk_2_2a367648:



    nvl clear
    "\n She's the type of person who guides others but lacks the bravery to act themselves. {w}Someone who finds it impossible to accept responsibility for their own influence."


translate English day12_hk_2_eb013fca:


    "Since meeting her, my religious belief has vanished. I've always found it impossible to worship people as gods."


translate English day12_hk_2_5a3065b5:


    "But I've found that I no longer believe in an all-mighty deity. {w}Like most people born and raised in the capital, I no longer hold out hope that my prayers will be answered."


translate English day12_hk_2_d3a271ce:


    et "She promised me trips to the city, across the ocean, to the moon itself, but do you think I believe she can actually follow through?"


translate English day12_hk_2_5bf97a1b:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'm scared of getting hurt by my own wishful thinking."


translate English day12_hk_2_813292a9:


    "I've continuously turned her down until now because I know I cannot walk with her on the path she must follow."


translate English day12_hk_2_2f5633bf:


    et "I'm sure she must know how much she has affected me by this point. {w}Though she's probably clueless as to where I will go from here."


translate English day12_hk_2_e4c57aa1:



    nvl clear
    "\n Just as I feared, I can no longer remain with her, and I can't support her moving forward either,"


translate English day12_hk_2_395cb7e8:


    et "and while I have fallen in love with Haku, I can't escape by forcing my decisions or my own opinions on others."


translate English day12_hk_2_f50d04a4:



    nvl clear
    "\n The reason why I, a woman, have fallen in love with her has nothing to do with her sexuality."


translate English day12_hk_2_f870d198:


    "I do not question her sense of righteousness, nor do I condemn her for the murderous acts she has committed."


translate English day12_hk_2_165838bd:


    et "She is no longer afraid. {w}And she no longer needs someone to rely on. She remains a pure and beautiful soul, even on her own. {w}And I can't stand it."


translate English day12_hk_2_5bbfc7dc:



    nvl clear
    "\n The path she chose is truly the right one, and while I was unable to walk it with her, I know it will lead her towards heroic deeds."


translate English day12_hk_2_9f826ef5:


    "Which is why I am telling you this."


translate English day12_hk_2_de0bac09:


    et "Coming to this dark hallway is like returning to those days when the world was always dark as night."


translate English day12_hk_2_1168c581:



    nvl clear
    "\n Oh, god... I feel dizzy. {w}Why am I suddenly this excited?"


translate English day12_hk_2_7f19fe87:


    "She will continue bringing justice to the world. Though the sins she's burdened with are too heavy for one person alone."


translate English day12_hk_2_5c59d2ba:


    et "I ask that you come to know her sin. {w}And that you cleanse her of it. {w}That's all."


translate English day12_hk_2_e710e951:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'm not here to lay blame... She no longer remembers the pain and the love she once felt so long ago, which is why there's no point in me clinging to my hatred."


translate English day12_hk_2_d5674b76:


    et "However, I am the only one who can speak on her sin. {w}Because I alone am the only person on Earth who knows the truth."


translate English day12_hk_2_bd0b637f:


    nar "My lips tremble faintly following the barrage of words that came tumbling out all at once. {w}I remain the only person in the hallway."


translate English day12_hk_2_77e8e7e3:


    nar "Not a single soul passes through."


translate English day12_hk_2_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_hk_2_69415637:


    sc "I'll be taking my leave then. {w}Your Eminence."


translate English day12_hk_2_eeba5b0b:


    nar "I bow deeply while standing before the door and then I make as if to leave."


translate English day12_hk_2_e9edef0c:


    nar "But when I raise my head once more, the door lies open."


translate English day12_hk_2_53cd076d:


    nar "Naturally, there is no light that spills out through the slightly gloomy doorway."


translate English day12_hk_2_701a0c93:


    nar "Instead, a pure-white hand slips through the gap."


translate English day12_hk_2_fd20828e:


    nar "I feel dizzy, almost as if the hand that suddenly appeared had punched me."


translate English day12_hk_2_560d0a05:


    nar "But it stops before me while holding a single bag, and I very carefully accept using both hands."


translate English day12_hk_2_ad7e9469:


    nar "I'm not sure if the voice I heard belonged to a man or not."


translate English day12_hk_2_1e046f3e:


    nar "And I have no idea if the hand was that of the Cardinal himself. {w}Hefting the bag in my palm, I can feel hard objects rolling around."


translate English day12_hk_2_677f7625:


    nar "The bag is full of silver coins."


translate English day12_hk_2_2dc43c03:


    sc "Oh..."


translate English day12_hk_2_a9162893:


    sc "Thanks..." with sshake


translate English day12_hk_2_b5272b2b:


    nar "I wander the temple alone. {w}Ever corner of the old building is colored by memories of her and I."


translate English day12_hk_2_81fe22e8:


    nar "The sound of two people laughing together as they engage in conversation about nothing in particular leaves my thoughts a chaotic mess. {w}And I run away in order to escape the shadows that exist there."


translate English day12_hk_2_f95b8990:


    nar "Water occasionally trickles down through the holes in my hot eyes, slowly melting my brain."


translate English day12_hk_2_1de55d42:


    nar "I wanted her."


translate English day12_hk_2_888b0670:


    nar "The lust that fills my entire body is so hot and sharp that I knew it would quickly become too big for me to handle, and that I'd eventually kill myself."


translate English day12_hk_2_c913fc53:


    nar "By the next morning, the residual heat had cooled down. It was as if the fever that had tormented me throughout the night was nothing more than a dream."


translate English day12_hk_2_35cb4122:


    nar "I head into town first thing in the morning and, reenacting a scene I once read in an old book, I use some of the money I received to buy clothes that were never touched by Haku."


translate English day12_hk_2_9397d8f0:


    nar "I splash cold water on my face, which is still somewhat painful, before taking the familiar path back to the temple."


translate English day12_hk_2_bd0c36d4:


    nar "There is no one around to tell me what I can and can't do anymore."


translate English day12_hk_2_21ac6429:


    nar "It's nine in the morning. {w}The bishops are hurrying down the hall to get to their meeting."


translate English day12_hk_2_70e66fde:


    nar "As they shuffle forward in single file, the priests bow their heads as if in prayer."


translate English day12_hk_2_d6363115:


    nar "The routine I've grown used to unfolds before my eyes."


translate English day12_hk_2_ba61fc15:


    nar "White hair tied back without a single strand out of place and her monastic robe without a single wrinkle. Her elegant stature I've come to know so well."


translate English day12_hk_2_d45aba36:


    nar "That beautiful woman walks lightly on her feet, as if she's never committed a single sin in her life."


translate English day12_hk_2_e2d55cdb:


    sc "Take a good look. That woman you see before you is the embodiment of Pestis."


translate English day12_hk_2_cdc8b448:


    nar "My voice rings out clearly, and everyone in the immediate area freezes."


translate English day12_hk_2_62d86262:


    sc "From her pure-white hair to her sudden assignment to the newly formed department. {w}Is no one even the slightest bit suspicious regarding any of it?"


translate English day12_hk_2_136e777c:


    sc "Have any of you seen her use the Sacred Techniques in front of you even once?"


translate English day12_hk_2_1e09fc72:


    sc "She was not blessed with the stigmata. It's as if her body itself denies the existence of God."


translate English day12_hk_2_733e5c3d:


    sc "And that's not all. {w}She's the one who murdered Arne Alternata."


translate English day12_hk_2_63d274d1:


    sc "She is a traitor who was never blessed by the grace of God, and the most depraved of all murderers."


translate English day12_hk_2_777f4906:


    sc "I know what she's done..."


translate English day12_hk_2_cbe26e67:


    nar "I pull back the black veil that covers my face and look at her. {w}Our eyes meet."


translate English day12_hk_2_69607095:


    sc "I'm sure the other bishops here are aware of that fact."


translate English day12_hk_2_9766b84b:


    sc "So why has the truth been intentionally covered up until now?"


translate English day12_hk_2_8e066d45:


    sc "She's committed a blatant crime. {w}No one should receive blessings from this swindler of a bishop, nor should they be forced to follow her orders."


translate English day12_hk_2_0865cb83:


    sc "If you doubt my word, then I implore you to call the authorities."


translate English day12_hk_2_60ad7ec0:


    sc "Tear the clothes from this visage of Pestis and remove her from her throne."


translate English day12_hk_2_88cf959a:


    sc "Let her be punished accordingly and face justice at our hands!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_2_afd96769:


    nar "A ripple of agitation passes through the crowd, turning into a roar."


translate English day12_hk_2_a290f767:


    nar "If I'm the only one who retains our shared memories thus forced to destroy the dreams I secretly hold,"


translate English day12_hk_2_6d111198:


    nar "then I want her to be forced to remember me, even in hatred."


translate English day12_hk_2_c3ac1ba5:


    nar "She looks at me anxiously, making it clear that the thought of this situation ever arising had never once crossed her mind."


translate English day12_hk_2_77f267e7:


    nar "It's the look of someone who has been betrayed."


translate English day12_hk_2_b081a839:


    nar "She probably thinks I betrayed her trust. {w}But honestly, this is your punishment for loving me."


translate English day12_hk_2_166683d3:


    hk_b "Hey... What do you think you're doing?! Unhand me!"


translate English day12_hk_2_b6168642:


    nar "A priest from the administrative department quickly arrives and apprehends her."


translate English day12_hk_2_0bd66529:


    nar "She could have easily broken free if she'd wanted to, and yet she doesn't put up much of a fight."


translate English day12_hk_2_5b667e86:


    nar "Her tone is oddly polite. {w}The other priests inadvertently block the hallway in their state of bewilderment."


translate English day12_hk_2_43a8224d:


    nar "Several priests back away, almost as if saying \"the time has come.\""


translate English day12_hk_2_dff183bb:


    nar "The world spins around me far more vividly than before, almost as if I've suddenly awoken from a strange dream."


translate English day12_hk_2_36520431:


    sc "The time of redemption has come! Now, justice will finally be served!" with sshake


translate English day12_hk_2_530a6992:


    nar "All of this is for the justice that she so badly needed to protect."


translate English day12_hk_2_95512aa9:


    nar "And in this way, every single one of her most precious secrets will be exposed."


translate English day12_hk_2_d2dfc641:


    nar "I hear the scattered screams of a couple women mixed with cheers from the crowd! {w}I raise my voice and laugh."


translate English day12_hk_2_35f20862:


    nar "The action causes my breasts to sway in response, though it no longer feels as uncomfortable as it once did."


translate English day12_hk_2_258985f7:


    nar "As a priest who devoted my life to God, this concludes my final mission. {w}It was done for a good cause."


translate English day12_hk_2_87399994:


    nar "It was never anything personal..."


